{"type":"message","id":"09e1e770","parentId":"a05f2ce9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T04:38:15.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问好了吗，现在子agent已经整理好了最新的Claude Code动态，我需要把结果展示给用户，按照要求只发一条总结消息，格式清晰。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] \n# 🚀 Claude Code 每日最新最热动态\n\n## 一、GitHub 热门项目\n\n| 项目名称 | Star 数量 | 核心亮点 |\n|---------|----------|---------|\n| **everything-claude-code** | 原版超 50K，中文翻译版 275+ | Anthropic 黑客马拉松获胜项目，包含 47 个专业代理、181 个技能、79 个命令 |\n| **claude-code-templates** | 24.3K | GitHub 最热门配置全家桶，一键安装，支持全栈多语言 |\n| **clawcode** | 超 11 万 | 架构同源但规避法律风险，GitHub 历史增速最快项目之一 |\n| **Caveman** | 2.9K | 帮 Claude Code 节省 65% token，上线 2 天冲上 HN 首页 |\n| **OH-MY-CLAUDECODE** | 快速增长 | 面向团队的多智能体编排工具，支持多实例协同 |\n\n更多项目看这里：\n- [yechan-Heo/oh-my-codex](https://github.com/Yeachan-Heo/oh-my-codex) - 多模型混合编排\n- [jarrodwatts/claude-hud](https://github.com/jarrodwatts/claude-hud) - 桌面交互界面\n- [shareAI-lab/learn-claude-code](https://github.com/shareAI-lab/learn-claude-code) - 最佳实践学习\n\n## 二、最新工具发布\n\n1. **Claude Code 官方 v1.0.62**（2025.7.29）已正式生产可用，支持 GitHub Actions 集成和全 IDE 原生扩展\n2. **Caveman** - 节省 65% token，兼容 Claude Code 和 OpenAI Codex\n3. **everything-claude-code** - 完整配置集合，支持自动持续学习\n4. **OH-MY-CLAUDECODE** - 团队级多智能体编排框架\n\n## 三、行业动态\n\n- Claude 生态正从单一 API 服务演变为完整开发者生态，近期社区项目爆发式增长\n- `clawcode` 成为 GitHub 历史增速最快开源项目之一，发布 1 天突破 10 万星\n- Claude Code 源码泄露事件后，社区对周边工具需求激增，推动生态快速发展\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":35846,"output":581,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39811,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775795884547}}
{"type":"message","id":"665144ed","parentId":"09e1e770","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:12:20.732Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 17:12:19 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25 [msg:om_x100b52bfa1e09cb4c43163564f08b56, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52bfa1e09cb4c43163564f08b56\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 17:12 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\"\n}\n```\n\n建一个新的定时任务，每天找 30 个跨境高溢价的商品,要求:\n1. 考虑汇率的情况下 15 倍溢价以上，比如水晶杯中国卖 80 元，在美国卖 200 刀\n2. 体积不能太大，成本不超过 100 人民币\n3. 主要在工艺品方向\n\n需要把商品的链接也返回给我，同时带上一定的分析"}],"timestamp":1775812340723}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a5d9751","parentId":"665144ed","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:12:43.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户现在需要新建一个定时任务，每天找30个跨境高溢价工艺品商品，满足溢价15倍以上，体积不大，成本不超过100元人民币，还要链接和分析。根据系统的能力，这个需要先搜索，然后定时推送。我需要用cron工具添加一个新的job。首先，先看一下cron add的参数，需要name，schedule，payload，delivery，sessionTarget。schedule是每天什么时候运行，用户没说时间，就默认每天早上10点吧。payload是agentTurn，message就是用户的要求，target还是用户自己。sessionTarget是isolated，delivery mode是announce，to是用户的open id。所以构造cron add。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] \n好的，我这就帮你创建一个定时任务，每天为你查找符合要求的跨境高溢价工艺品商品。\n\n🦞\n</think_never_used_51bce0c785ca2f68081bfa7d91973934>"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_r6vgb4gsigax14dauulizxjs","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"\n        \"add\"\n      ","job":{"name":"每日跨境高溢价工艺品商品推送","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 10 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请帮我搜索并整理30个符合以下要求的跨境高溢价商品：1. 考虑汇率情况下溢价15倍以上 2. 体积不大，成本不超过100元人民币 3. 主要在工艺品方向。请为每个商品提供名称、国内成本、海外售价、溢价倍数、商品链接和简要分析，整理成清晰的Markdown格式推送给用户ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25。","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enabled":true}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":17707,"output":487,"cacheRead":28472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46666,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775812340727}}
