{"type":"message","id":"9978e61d","parentId":"a77e33d4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:24:14.448Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01Kr8WmuUKqZoqNuF6hrUE5y","toolName":"miaoda_web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"DS-160 填写助手 工具 在线填写 自动填表\",\n  \"provider\": \"miaoda\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"How DS-160 Automation Works | Save 2+ Hours on Your Visa Application | DS-160 Made Simple\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ds160.io/\",\n      \"description\": \"Answer questions in our intuitive interface that saves automatically. No timeouts, work at your own pace.\\n02\\nChoose Consulate & Submit\\nSelect any US consulate worldwide. We autofill your CEAC form and guide you to submit.\\n03\\nCopy Application ID & Book Appointment\\nGet your DS-160 confirmation number and use it to schedule your visa interview at the embassy.\\nWatch Our Process in Action\\nSee exactly how we simplify your DS-160...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"如何填写美国旅游签证申请表格?去哪里填写?_旅游签证问题_美国签证中心网站\",\n      \"url\": \"http://www.meiguo-qianzheng.com/lvyouqianzhengwenti/67.html\",\n      \"description\": \"申请美国旅游签证只需要填写DS-160申请表格，DS-160只能在线填写，没有样板下载。请您用英文填写，如果您...\\n\\n请注意： 如您不懂得如何填写，我们可以提供中文填写 DS-160申请表服务，选择此项服务的申请人须用中文填写资料表，并在线提交给我们，我们收到申请人中文信息内登陆美国国务院网站完成英文DS-160申请表，并发确认页给申请人。\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"【攻略】如何快速填写DS-160表?填DS-160表要注意什么?\",\n      \"url\": \"https://zoular.com/articles/425?ref=index\",\n      \"description\": \"官网填写3小时，走啦AI辅助填写10分钟！\\n\\n通常第一次自己官网填DS-160哪怕对照着攻略也最少要花3小时的时间。\\n但如果使用「走啦AI辅助填表系统」：\\n\\n只需上传护照，护照信息自动识别，避免输入错误。\\n没有电脑也能填，手机打字输入入中文相关信息，老年人也能轻松操作。\\n行程计划自动生成，酒店信息自动匹配，省心高效。...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"AI智能填表助手 - 基于DeepSeek的Web表单自动填写工具_ai填表助手-CSDN博客\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_27346503/article/details/151805874\",\n      \"description\": \"全面支持表单控件：能够自动识别并填写各种类型的网页表单控件，包括文本框、日期选择器、下拉框、复选框甚至是附件上传...\\n跨平台操作便捷：支持从本地文件、微信聊天记录或直接截图上传图片，快速提取内容并完成表单填写，非常贴合日常使用习惯。\\n一键自动填表：智能匹配表单字段，只需点击一下，就能自动完成所有填写工作，极大提升效率，还能有效减少人为错误。\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"v0 App\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ds160.site/en\",\n      \"description\": \"DS-160 AI Assistant\\nU.S. Visa Application Helper\\nOfficial DS-160 Form Assistance\\nComplete Your DS-160 Visa Application\\nGet step-by-step AI guidance through the official U.S. DS-160 visa application form. Our assistant helps you provide accurate information, validates your answers, and ensures your application is complete.\\nCreate an account to save your progress and return anytime\\n2\\nChat with AI\\nAnswer questions one by one through our...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"I Built a Tool for Filling Out the US Visa DS160 Form\",\n      \"url\": \"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=44319685\",\n      \"description\": \"Built for anyone who’s had the pleasure of experiencing US visa process.\\nI'm sharing a solo project I've been working on called DS160.io. It's a tool for people applying for US visas who are tired of the broken experience on...\\nYou can complete a new DS-160 in under 5 minutes this way, and the tool will fill it out in under a minute.\\n3. Making it easier to complete DS-160s for dependents. \",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Automate DS-160 Filing\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ds160.io/agencies\",\n      \"description\": \"Review and approve all client responses before DS-160 submission. Make amendments, add notes, and maintain full control over accuracy.\\nMulti-Language Support\\nQuestionnaires available in 6+ languages including English, Spanish, Russian, Chinese, Vietnamese, and Romanian with more coming soon. Critical details like passport info stay in English. AI translation coming soon.\\n3\\nReview & Approve Submissions\\nAll forms appear in your dashboard for review with AI translations from their native language to English...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"I'm working on Fillvisa.com - a free, browser-based tool that lets you fill comp...\",\n      \"url\": \"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=45884575\",\n      \"description\": \"I'm working on Fillvisa.com - a free, browser-based tool that lets you fill complex U.S. immigration forms (like DS-160, AR-11, I-90, etc.) entirely in your browser.\\nIt mimics the official USCIS forms but autosaves locally, validates inputs, and lets you download a ready-to-submit PDF - no signup, no uploads, no tracking.\\nIt’s meant for travelers and immigrants who just need to...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"US Immigration Visa & Travel Services DS-160 B1/B2 US Visa Application 2010-2025 free printable template\",\n      \"url\": \"https://ds-160-visa-form.pdffiller.com/\",\n      \"description\": \"01 To fill out the DS 160 blank form, you will first need to access the official U.S. Department of State website.\\n02 Once on the website, locate the DS 160 form and click on it to begin the application process.\\n03 Follow the instructions provided and enter all the required personal information accurately. This may include your full name, date of birth, nationality, passport information, and contact details among others.\\n04 Provide information about...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"美国旅游签证的DS-160申请表上的美国联系人怎么填写?_旅游签证问题_美国签证中心网站\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.meiguo-qianzheng.com/lvyouqianzhengwenti/801.html\",\n      \"description\": \"申请美国旅游签证时，DS-160申请表上的美国联系人可以填写在美的亲属或朋友，如没有，可以填写您想入住的酒店信息，关系选择“other”。\\nU.S. Point of Contact Information 美国联系人信息填写： - 如美国有具体联系人（或组织），需填写联系人的姓名（或组织名称）及与您的关系...\\n- 若无则直接填写酒店信息，关系选择“other”。如图：\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"DS-160 填写助手 工具 在线填写 自动填表","provider":"miaoda","count":10,"results":[{"title":"How DS-160 Auto