{"type":"message","id":"cd61bf4f","parentId":"b004a22f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:24:23.985Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01M22bHa96MHRjbCciGB9nNh","toolName":"miaoda_web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"DS160.io 价格 收费 功能 评价\",\n  \"provider\": \"miaoda\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"DS160 Form Pilot\",\n      \"url\": \"https://launchtory.com/projects/ds160-io\",\n      \"description\": \"DS160 Form Pilot\\nMaking DS-...\\n\\nAutomate your DS160 submission | DS160.io\\nds160.io\\nDS160.io offers a painless way to complete your DS-160 visa application. It prevents timeouts, saves progress as you go, and lets you reuse previous applications for faster submissions. Ideal for e...\\nTopics in DS160 Form Pilot\\nVisa Application\\nTravel\\nAutomation\\nForm Filling\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"DS160 USA\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ds160usa.com/\",\n      \"description\": \"M visa For trainees/students in non-academic training programs (vocational training)...\\nEmail recovery of your DS-l60 in case of loss.\\nFixed price $165 per application. Multiple Global methods of payment accepted: VisaCard, Mastercard, Amex, JCB, Maestro, Discover, Diners Club, Alipay, WeChat, UnionPay. (MRV Fee not included)\\nApproved Insurance Policy. Refund if your travel authorization is denied\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"DS-260 vs DS-160: Key Differences for Immigrant and Nonimmigrant Visas\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.visaverge.com/visa/ds-260-vs-ds-160-key-differences-for-immigrant-and-nonimmigrant-visas/\",\n      \"description\": \"DS-160 — no submission fee for the form itself, but applicants must pay the standard visa application fee for their visa category.\\nDS-160 is for temporary visits and requires a printed confirmation and visa fee payment; DS-260 requires $325 processing plus $120 for the affidavit of support (total $445) paid to the NVC before filing and mandates English answers in Roman characters. DS-260 cannot be edited online...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Login | DS-160 Made Simple\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ds160.io/login\",\n      \"description\": \"Loading...\\nDS160.io\\nDS160.io\\nHomePricingAgenciesBlogResources\\nEnglishLoading...\\nOpen main menu\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"DS-160 Basics\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ds160.io/resources/about-the-ds160\",\n      \"description\": \"DS-160 Basics\\nWhat is a DS-160 Form?\\nWhat is the DS-160 number?\\nHow long does the DS-160 last?\\nWhen does the DS-160 expire?\\nHow long is the DS-160 valid?\\nCan the DS-160 be edited?\\nCan the DS-160 be updated after submission?\\nCan the DS-160 be updated after scheduling an...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"DS 160 Online Visa Application | USA Visas Services\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.usa-visas-services.com/ds-160-for-us-visas\",\n      \"description\": \"The Premium Service Offers 100% Refund Guarantee\\nin Case of a Denied Visa*\\n+\\nThe following Benefits that the Government website doesn't offer:\\nMultilingual Form (15 languages)\\n100% Refund if your visa is denied, including the Government fees.\\nNo registration or login required.\\nThe Premium Processing fee: $165 does not include the MRV Fee that needs to be paid to the Department of State for your interview.\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"美国签证DS160-全国受理\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.aavisa.com/VISA/Product/Detail?VisaId=9133500b625a42859cbc7af1e277dd69\",\n      \"description\": \"￥99\\n客户可自主填写或加密转发给他人协助填写（如亲属、同事），数据实时同步。\\n双阶审核机制\\n初审：专业客服团队核验表格完整性及逻辑一致性，标注缺失/存疑项；\\n补正：如果填写信息有缺失则打回重新补充，确保符合使馆规范。\\n官方数据转换与提交\\n审核...\\n2、填表成功后，如因客户自身原因要修改表格内容，费用重新收取；\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"DS160 USA-Visasforms Visa Application\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.visasforms.com/en/countries/ds160-usa/?email=user%40example.com&nationality=CN\",\n      \"description\": \"• Verification/validation of additional information.\\n• 24/7...\\n• Your approved DS-160 confirmation page sent in PDF format\\n• Email recovery of your DS-l60 in case of loss.\\n• Fixed price $149 per application. Multiple Global methods of payment accepted: VisaCard, Mastercard, Amex, JCB, Maestro, Discover, Diners Club, Alipay, WeChat, UnionPay. (MRV Fee not included)\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"How to Fill Out Form DS-160 for a U.S. Visa\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.boundless.com/immigration-resources/form-ds-160-explained/\",\n      \"description\": \"If not, you must reschedule with the correct number.\\nForm DS-160 Cost and Visa Fees\\nThere is no fee to file the DS-160 form itself. However, you will still need to pay a processing fee for the specific visa you are applying for. This fee varies depending on the visa type and can be found on the U.S. Department of State website.\\nNon-Petition-Based Visas\\nFor most non-petition-based nonimmigrant visas...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Pricing\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.birdctl.com/pricing\",\n      \"description\": \"Pricing\\n$10\\nSaves you 120 minutes on each DS-160 form.\\nSingle Form\\n$10 per form\\nPerfect for individuals.\\nNo more time wasted on DS150 timeouts.\\nWorks for all visa types F-1, H-1B, E-3 and many more.\\nYour DS160 form filled out in seconds.\\nThe last DS160 you will ever complete.\\nThree or...\\n\",\n      \"siteName\": \"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"DS160.io 价格 收费 功能 评价","provider":"miaoda","count":10,"results":[{"title":"DS160 Form Pilot","url":"https://launchtory.com/projects/ds160-io","description":"DS160 Form Pilot\nMaking DS-...\n\nAutomate your DS160 submission | DS160.io\nds160.io\nDS160.io offers a painless way to complete your DS-160 visa application. It prevents timeouts, saves progress as you go, and lets you reuse previous applications for faster submissions. Ideal for e...\nTopics in DS160 Form Pilot\nVisa Application\nTravel\nAutomation\nForm Filling\n","siteName":""},{"title":"DS160 USA","url":"https://www.ds160usa.com/","description":"M visa For trainees/students in non-academic training programs (vocational training)...\nEmail recovery of your DS-l60 in case of loss.\nFixed price $165 per application. Multiple Global methods of payment accepted: VisaCard, Mastercard, Amex, JCB, Maestro, Discover, Diners Club, Alipay, WeChat, UnionPay. (MRV Fee not included)\nApproved Insurance Policy. Refund if your travel authorization is denied\n","siteName":""},{"title":"DS-260 vs DS-160: Key Differences for Immigrant and Nonimmigrant Visas","url":"https://www.visaverge.com/visa/ds-260-vs-ds-160-key-differences-for-immigrant-and-nonimmigrant-visas/","description":"DS-160 — no submission fee for the form itself, but applicants must pay the standard visa application fee for their visa category.\nDS-160 is for temporary visits and requires a printed confirmation and visa fee payment; DS-260 requires $325 processing plus $120 for the affidavit of support (total $445) paid to the NVC before filing and mandates English answers in Roman characters. DS-260 cannot be edited online...\n","siteName":""},{"title":"Login | DS-160 Made Simple","url":"https://www.ds160.io/login","description":"Loading...\nDS160.io\nDS160.io\nHomePricingAgenciesBlogResources\nEnglishLoading...\nOpen main menu","siteName":""},{"title":"DS-160 Basics","url":"https://www.ds160.io/resources/about-the-ds160","description":"DS-160 Basics\nWhat is a DS-160 Form?\nWhat is the DS-160 number?\nHow long does the DS-160 last?\nWhen does the DS-160 expire?\nHow long is the DS-160 valid?\nCan the DS-160 be edited?\nCan the DS-160 be updated after submission?\nCan the DS-160 be updated after scheduling an...\n","siteName":""},{"title":"DS 160 Online Visa Application | USA Visas Services","url":"https://www.usa-visas-services.com/ds-160-for-us-visas","description":"The Premium Service Offers 100% Refund Guarantee\nin Case of a Denied Visa*\n+\nThe following Benefits that the Government website doesn't offer:\nMultilingual Form (15 languages)\n100% Refund if your visa is denied, including the Government fees.\nNo registration or login required.\nThe Premium Processing fee: $165 does not include the MRV Fee that needs to be paid to the Department of State for your interview.\n","siteName":""},{"title":"美国签证DS160-全国受理","url":"https://www.aavisa.com/VISA/Product/Detail?VisaId=9133500b625a42859cbc7af1e277dd69","description":"￥99\n客户可自主填写或加密转发给他人协助填写（如亲属、同事），数据实时同步。\n双阶审核机制\n初审：专业客服团队核验表格完整性及逻辑一致性，标注缺失/存疑项；\n补正：如果填写信息有缺失则打回重新补充，确保符合使馆规范。\n官方数据转换与提交\n审核...\n2、填表成功后，如因客户自身原因要修改表格内容，费用重新收取；\n","siteName":""},{"title":"DS160 USA-Visasforms Visa Application","url":"https://www.visasforms.com/en/countries/ds160-usa/?email=user%40example.com&nationality=CN","description":"• Verification/validation of additional information.\n• 24/7...\n• Your approved DS-160 confirmation page sent in PDF format\n• Email recovery of your DS-l60 in case of loss.\n• Fixed price $149 per application. Multiple Global methods of payment accepted: VisaCard, Mastercard, Amex, JCB, Maestro, Discover, Diners Club, Alipay, WeChat, UnionPay. (MRV Fee not included)\n","siteName":""},{"title":"How to Fill Out Form DS-160 for a U.S. Visa","url":"https://www.boundless.com/immigration-resources/form-ds-160-explained/","description":"If not, you must reschedule with the correct number.\nForm DS-160 Cost and Visa Fees\nThere is no fee to file the DS-160 form itself. However, you will still need to pay a processing fee for the specific visa you are applying for. This fee varies depending on the visa type and can be found on the U.S. Department of State website.\nNon-Petition-Based Visas\nFor most non-petition-based nonimmigrant visas...\n","siteName":""},{"title":"Pricing","url":"https://www.birdctl.com/pricing","description":"Pricing\n$10\nSaves you 120 minutes on each DS-160 form.\nSingle Form\n$10 per form\nPerfect for individuals.\nNo more time wasted on DS150 timeouts.\nWorks for all visa types F-1, H-1B, E-3 and many more.\nYour DS160 form filled out in seconds.\nThe last DS160 you will ever complete.\nThree or...\n","siteName":""}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775831063978}}
