{"type":"compaction","id":"4bb15d4e","parentId":"590ea29d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T15:01:30.710Z","summary":"## Goal\n- User wants a daily cron task that finds 30 cross-border high-margin craft products meeting specific criteria\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Products must have 15x+ price markup (considering exchange rate) - example: crystal cup costs ¥80 in China, sells for $200 in USA\n- Volume must be small, cost under ¥100 RMB\n- Focus on craft/artisan products direction\n- Must include product links and analysis\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Checked existing cron jobs - found \"每日推送claudecode最热动态\" (runs daily 9:00 AM)\n- [x] Manually triggered claudecode daily push task after user asked about missing push\n- [x] Generated Claude Code latest updates via subagent (completed successfully)\n- [x] Created new cron job \"每日跨境高溢价工艺品商品推送\" with ID `1dace71d-52e3-469e-8325-7c74da11bc41`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Verifying new cron task is properly enabled (user asking \"可以了吗\")\n\n### Blocked\n- Tool call format error when trying to list cron jobs (action parameter format issue)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Cron schedule**: Set to 10:00 AM daily (Asia/Shanghai timezone) since user didn't specify time\n- **Task timeout**: Set to 600 seconds given complexity of finding 30 products with links and analysis\n- **Delivery mode**: announce via Feishu DM to user\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Successfully call `cron(action=\"list\", includeDisabled=true)` with correct parameter format to verify job creation\n2. Confirm task is enabled and show next run time to user\n3. Optionally offer to manually trigger first run if user wants immediate results\n\n## Critical Context\n- User ID: `ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25`\n- New cron job ID: `1dace71d-52e3-469e-8325-7c74da11bc41`\n- Job name: \"每日跨境高溢价工艺品商品推送\"\n- Schedule: `0 10 * * *` (cron expression)\n- Next scheduled run: `1775873025189` (timestamp in ms)\n- Task payload message: \"请帮我搜索并整理30个符合以下要求的跨境高溢价商品：1. 考虑汇率情况下溢价15倍以上 2. 体积不大，