ig/agents_config.yaml` and `config/models_config.yaml`\n- [ ] Create `workflows/saas_development.py` workflow definition\n- [ ] Create `tools/` directory with code_executor.py, file_manager.py, git_operations.py\n- [ ] Create agent module files in `agents/` directory\n- [ ] Create `outputs/` directory structure (code/, docs/, logs/)\n- [ ] Test the main.py script with actual API keys\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Medium difficulty small SaaS application\n- Must include Chrome plugin and lightweight front-end/back-end\n- Expected user scale: 1000-10000 users\n- Code must use TypeScript strict mode, be component/modular, include detailed comments, follow best practices\n- Security requirements: input validation, SQL injection protection, XSS protection, CSRF protection\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User requested: \"挑一个强大的 agent 开发团队准备一下\" (pick a powerful agent development team and prepare it)\n- No further clarification requested yet on specific features or preferences beyond the TabManager Pro example\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- **Message ID**: `om_x100b52b8e92c7084c3dcf032c25ddfd`\n- **Sender ID**: `ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25`\n- **Timestamp**: `2026-04-10 18:01:34 GMT+8`\n- **Model**: `claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022`\n- **Files created**: \n  - `agent-dev-team/README.md` (2907 bytes)\n  - `agent-dev-team/main.py` (5630 bytes)\n  - `agent-dev-team/requirements.txt` (238 bytes)\n- **Work directory**: `outputs/code`\n- **Project name example**: `TabManager Pro`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: System: [2026-04-10 17:20:41 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25 [msg:om_x100b52b840458484c4eefde059e3c04]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52b840458484c4eefde059e3c04\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 17:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  