{"type":"message","id":"0ec18bff","parentId":"7813a128","timestamp":"2026-04-10T15:27:12.092Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！现在我需要GitHub的访问信息。让我整理一下需要的信息并配置AG2：\n\n[[reply_to_current]]\n# 🔧 配置AG2团队 + GitHub同步\n\n## 我已获取到的信息 ✅\n\n### Erda API配置\n- **Base URL**: https://ai-proxy.erda.cloud/v1\n- **API Key**: t_4e0ca0463fad462d9687ce501ee00e84\n- **Model**: anthropic/us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0\n\n### GitHub仓库\n- **Repo**: https://github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git\n\n---\n\n## 我还需要的信息 🔑\n\n### 1. GitHub认证信息（二选一）\n\n**选项A：Personal Access Token（推荐）**\n- GitHub Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens\n- 需要权限：`repo`（完整仓库访问权限）\n- 格式：`ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxx`\n\n**选项B：SSH密钥**\n- 如果你已配置SSH密钥到GitHub\n- 我可以用系统的SSH密钥推送\n\n### 2. Git用户信息\n- **用户名**：你的GitHub用户名（用于commit）\n- **邮箱**：你的GitHub邮箱（用于commit）\n\n---\n\n## 快速检查\n\n让我先检查系统是否已配置Git：\n\n🦞"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_0145LyrgTTG7FkTuN9GfiY2U","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git config --global user.name && git config --global user.email"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"erda","model":"anthropic/us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0","usage":{"input":139326,"output":467,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775834818776}}
