{"type":"message","id":"f38bb9cd","parentId":"1ae359e9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:08:12.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的！我明白了，你希望在飞书聊天界面中看到消息的时间戳。不过这个显示是由飞书客户端控制的，我作为AI助手无法直接修改飞书的UI显示。\n\n但我可以在我的回复中主动带上时间信息！从现在开始，我会在重要的更新消息中标注时间。\n\n让我现在就查看一下AG2的最新进度："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_016KsAkCVhkjnK1SzeyyTbDv","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"young-river","timeout":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"erda","model":"anthropic/us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0","usage":{"input":155540,"output":220,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155760,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775837281576}}
{"type":"message","id":"44f00c1f","parentId":"f38bb9cd","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:08:17.700Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_016KsAkCVhkjnK1SzeyyTbDv","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"）\n**目标：** 完成应用页面框架\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 应用布局（侧边栏导航）\n- ✅ Dashboard页面\n- ✅ 草稿管理页面\n- ✅ Pinia stores基础结构\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 可以创建新草稿\n- 草稿列表正常显示\n- localStorage保存/读取正常\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 3: 核心表单（Day 3-5）\n**目标：** 完成12步表单填写\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 12个步骤页面\n- ✅ 表单组件库\n- ✅ 实时校验功能\n- ✅ 高风险字段警告\n- ✅ 自动保存功能\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 可以完整走完12个步骤\n- 表单数据正确保存到localStorage\n- 高风险字段显示橙色警告\n- 步骤导航显示进度\n- 实时校验提示错误\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 4: MVP完成（Day 6）\n**目标：** 完整可用的MVP版本\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 所有功能模块\n- ✅ UI组件库\n- ✅ 完整文档\n- ✅ QA测试通过\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 用户可以从头到尾完成表单填写\n- 草稿管理功能正常\n- 模拟同步功能正常（计数）\n- 移动端体验良好\n- 代码质量检查通过\n- README文档完整\n\n---\n\n## 五、技术规范\n\n### 5.1 代码规范\n```typescript\n// 文件命名：kebab-case\n// 组件命名：PascalCase\n// 函数命名：camelCase\n// 常量命名：UPPER_SNAKE_CASE\n\n// TypeScript严格模式\n// ESLint + Prettier\n```\n\n### 5.2 Git提交规范\n```\nfeat: 新功能\nfix: 修复bug\ndocs: 文档更新\nstyle: 代码格式调整\nrefactor: 重构\ntest: 测试\nchore: 构建/工具链\n```\n\n### 5.3 目录结构\n```\noutputs/ds160-helper/\n├── .nuxt/                  # Nuxt构建缓存\n├── components/             # Vue组件\n│   ├── app/               # 应用组件\n│   ├── form/              # 表单组件\n│   ├── marketing/         # 营销组件\n│   └── ui/                # UI组件库\n├── layouts/               # 布局\n├── pages/                 # 路由页面\n│   ├── app/              # 应用页面（CSR）\n│   └── *.vue             # 营销页面（SSR）\n├── stores/                # Pinia状态管理\n├── types/                 # TypeScript类型定义\n├── utils/                 # 工具函数\n├── public/                # 静态资源\n├── nuxt.config.ts         # Nuxt配置\n├── tailwind.config.js     # Tailwind配置\n├── package.json           # 依赖配置\n└── README.md              # 项目文档\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、风险评估\n\n### 高风险项\n1. **localStorage容量限制**\n   - 风险：表单数据可能超过5MB限制\n   - 缓解：数据压缩、分块存储\n\n2. **表单校验复杂度**\n   - 风险：12步骤联动校验逻辑复杂\n   - 缓解：模块化校验、单元测试\n\n3. **移动端体验**\n   - 风险：复杂表单在小屏幕上难用\n   - 缓解：响应式设计、渐进式展示\n\n### 中风险项\n1. **浏览器兼容性**\n   - 风险：部分API不兼容旧浏览器\n   - 缓解：Polyfill、浏览器检测\n\n2. **性能优化**\n   - 风险：大量表单字段影响性能\n   - 缓解：虚拟滚动、懒加载\n\n---\n\n## 七、下一步行动\n\n### 👨💻 Frontend Developer\n**现在开始开发！**\n\n请按以下顺序生成代码：\n\n1. **第一批文件（基础架构）**\n   - package.json\n   - nuxt.config.ts\n   - tsconfig.json\n   - tailwind.config.js\n   - types/index.ts\n\n2. **第二批文件（布局和营销页面）**\n   - layouts/default.vue\n   - layouts/app.vue\n   - pages/index.vue\n   - pages/features.vue\n   - pages/pricing.vue\n\n3. **第三批文件（应用页面）**\n   - pages/app/dashboard.vue\n   - pages/app/drafts.vue\n   - components/app/*\n\n4. **第四批文件（表单系统）**\n   - pages/app/form/step-*.vue\n   - components/form/*\n   - stores/*\n\n5. **第五批文件（UI组件和工具）**\n   - components/ui/*\n   - utils/*\n\n6. **第六批文件（文档）**\n   - README.md\n   - docs/*\n\n---\n\n**所有代码必须写入 `outputs/ds160-helper/` 目录**\n\n开始开发吧！💪\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: FrontendDeveloper\n\n[33m[autogen.oai.client: 04-11 00:07:36] {329} WARNING - Model us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0 is not found. The cost will be 0. In your config_list, add field {\"price\" : [prompt_price_per_1k, completion_token_price_per_1k]} for customized pricing.[0m\nFrontendDeveloper (to chat_manager):\n\n# Frontend Developer - 开始开发 DS-160 Helper MVP\n\n我将按照Product Manager的规划，逐步生成完整的Nuxt 3项目代码。\n\n---\n\n## 第一批文件：基础架构\n\n### 1. package.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"ds160-helper\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"DS-160 Helper MVP - 美国签证申请表辅助填写工具\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"nuxt dev\",\n    \"build\": \"nuxt build\",\n    \"generate\": \"nuxt generate\",\n    \"preview\": \"nuxt preview\",\n    \"postinstall\": \"nuxt prepare\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"nuxt typecheck\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@nuxt/icon\": \"^1.0.0\",\n    \"@pinia/nuxt\": \"^0.5.1\",\n    \"nuxt\": \"^3.11.2\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^2.1.7\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.4.21\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.3.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@nuxt/eslint-config\": \"^0.3.0\",\n    \"@nuxtjs/tailwindcss\": \"^6.12.0\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^20.12.7\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.57.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.5\",\n    \"vue-tsc\": \"^2.0.13\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. nuxt.config.ts\n\n```typescript\n// https://nuxt.com/docs/api/configuration/nuxt-config\nexport default defineNuxtConfig({\n  devtools: { enabled: true },\n  \n  modules: [\n    '@nuxtjs/tailwindcss',\n    '@pinia/nuxt',\n    '@nuxt/icon'\n  ],\n\n  // TypeScript配置\n  typescript: {\n    strict: true,\n    typeCheck: true\n  },\n\n  // 路由配置：SSR/CSR分离\n  routeRules: {\n    // 营销页面使用SSR\n    '/': { ssr: true },\n    '/features': { ssr: true },\n    '/pricing': { ssr: true },\n    \n    // 应用页面使用CSR\n    '/app/**': { ssr: false }\n  },\n\n  // App配置\n  app: {\n    head: {\n      title: 'DS-160 Helper - 美国签证申请表辅助工具',\n      meta: [\n        { charset: 'utf-8' },\n        { name: 'viewport', content: 'width=device-width, initial-scale=1' },\n        { \n          name: 'description', \n          content: '简化DS-160表单填写流程，智能提示高风险字段，自动保存草稿，让签证申请更轻松' \n        }\n      ],\n      link: [\n        { rel: 'icon', type: 'image/x-icon', href: '/favicon.ico' }\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n\n  // CSS配置\n  css: [\n    '~/assets/css/main.css'\n  ],\n\n  // Tailwind CSS配置\n  tailwindcss: {\n    cssPath: '~/assets/css/main.css',\n    configPath: 'tailwind.config.js',\n    exposeConfig: false,\n    viewer: true\n  },\n\n  // 构建配置\n  vite: {\n    vue: {\n      script: {\n        defineModel: true,\n        propsDestructure: true\n      }\n    }\n  },\n\n  // 兼容性日期\n  compatibilityDate: '2024-04-03'\n})\n```\n\n### 3. tsconfig.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"./.nuxt/tsconfig.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"noUnusedLocals\": true,\n    \"noUnusedParameters\": true,\n    \"noImplicitReturns\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"bundler\",\n    \"resolveJsonModule\": true,\n    \"allowSyntheticDefaultImports\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"types\": [\n      \"node\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"include\": [\n    \"**/*\",\n    \".nuxt/**/*\"\n  ],\n  \"exclude\": [\n    \"node_modules\",\n    \".nuxt\",\n    \"dist\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 4. tailwind.config.js\n\n```javascript\n/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */\nexport default {\n  content: [\n    \"./components/**/*.{js,vue,ts}\",\n    \"./layouts/**/*.vue\",\n    \"./pages/**/*.vue\",\n    \"./plugins/**/*.{js,ts}\",\n    \"./app.vue\",\n    \"./error.vue\",\n  ],\n  theme: {\n    extend: {\n      colors: {\n        primary: {\n          50: '#eff6ff',\n          100: '#dbeafe',\n          200: '#bfdbfe',\n          300: '#93c5fd',\n          400: '#60a5fa',\n          500: '#3b82f6',\n          600: '#2563eb',\n          700: '#1d4ed8',\n          800: '#1e40af',\n          900: '#1e3a8a',\n          950: '#172554',\n        },\n        warning: {\n          50: '#fff7ed',\n          100: '#ffedd5',\n          200: '#fed7aa',\n          300: '#fdba74',\n          400: '#fb923c',\n          500: '#f97316',\n          600: '#ea580c',\n          700: '#c2410c',\n          800: '#9a3412',\n          900: '#7c2d12',\n          950: '#431407',\n        }\n      },\n      fontFamily: {\n        sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],\n      },\n      animation: {\n        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out',\n        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.3s ease-out',\n        'slide-down': 'slideDown 0.3s ease-out',\n      },\n      keyframes: {\n        fadeIn: {\n          '0%': { opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { opacity: '1' },\n        },\n        slideUp: {\n          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(10px)', opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },\n        },\n        slideDown: {\n          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(-10px)', opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n  plugins: [],\n}\n```\n\n### 5. assets/css/main.css\n\n```css\n@tailwind base;\n@tailwind components;\n@tailwind utilities;\n\n@layer base {\n  * {\n    @apply border-border;\n  }\n  \n  body {\n    @apply bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 antialiased;\n  }\n\n  h1 {\n    @apply text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h2 {\n    @apply text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h3 {\n    @apply text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h4 {\n    @apply text-xl font-semibold;\n  }\n}\n\n@layer components {\n  /* 自定义滚动条 */\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n    @apply w-2;\n  }\n\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n    @apply bg-gray-100;\n  }\n\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n    @apply bg-gray-300 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-400;\n  }\n\n  /* 表单输入通用样式 */\n  .form-input {\n    @apply w-full px-4 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg \n           focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 \n           transition-colors duration-200 outline-none;\n  }\n\n  .form-input-error {\n    @apply border-red-500 focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500;\n  }\n\n  .form-input-warning {\n    @apply border-warning-500 focus:ring-warning-500 focus:border-warning-500;\n  }\n\n  /* 按钮基础样式 */\n  .btn {\n    @apply px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200 \n           focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 \n           disabled:cursor-not-allowed;\n  }\n\n  .btn-primary {\n    @apply btn bg-primary-600 text-white hover:bg-primary-700 \n           focus:ring-primary-500 active:bg-primary-800;\n  }\n\n  .btn-secondary {\n    @apply btn bg-gray-200 text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-300 \n           focus:ring-gray-500;\n  }\n\n  .btn-danger {\n    @apply btn bg-red-600 text-white hover:bg-red-700 \n           focus:ring-red-500;\n  }\n\n  .btn-outline {\n    @apply btn border-2 border-primary-600 text-primary-600 \n           hover:bg-primary-50 focus:ring-primary-500;\n  }\n}\n\n@layer utilities {\n  .text-balance {\n    text-wrap: balance;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 6. types/index.ts\n\n```typescript\n/**\n * DS-160 Helper - TypeScript类型定义\n */\n\n// ============================================\n// 草稿相关类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 草稿状态\n */\nexport type DraftStatus = 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'archived'\n\n/**\n * 草稿接口\n */\nexport interface Draft {\n  id: string\n  createdAt: Date\n  updatedAt: Date\n  currentStep: number // 1-12\n  status: DraftStatus\n  syncCount: number // 已使用的同步次数\n  data: FormData\n}\n\n/**\n * 创建草稿的输入参数\n */\nexport interface CreateDraftInput {\n  data?: Partial<FormData>\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 表单数据类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 完整表单数据\n */\nexport interface FormData {\n  step1?: Step1Data\n  step2?: Step2Data\n  step3?: Step3Data\n  step4?: Step4Data\n  step5?: Step5Data\n  step6?: Step6Data\n  step7?: Step7Data\n  step8?: Step8Data\n  step9?: Step9Data\n  step10?: Step10Data\n  step11?: Step11Data\n  step12?: Step12Data\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 1: 个人信息\n */\nexport interface Step1Data {\n  // 基本信息\n  surname: string // 姓（拼音）\n  givenName: string // 名（拼音）\n  surnameZh?: string // 姓（中文）\n  givenNameZh?: string // 名（中文）\n  fullNameNative?: string // 母语全名\n  \n  // 高风险字段\n  hasOtherNames: boolean // 是否有曾用名/别名\n  otherNames?: OtherName[] // 曾用名列表\n  \n  // 其他信息\n  gender: 'M' | 'F' | 'X' // 性别\n  maritalStatus: 'single' | 'married' | 'divorced' | 'widowed' | 'separated' // 婚姻状态\n  dateOfBirth: string // 出生日期 YYYY-MM-DD\n  cityOfBirth: string // 出生城市\n  provinceOfBirth: string // 出生省份\n  countryOfBirth: string // 出生国家\n  nationality: string // 国籍\n}\n\nexport interface OtherName {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  type: 'maiden' | 'previous' | 'alias' // 娘家姓/曾用名/别名\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 2: 护照信息\n */\nexport interface Step2Data {\n  passportNumber: string // 护照号码\n  passportBookNumber?: string // 护照本编号（如有）\n  countryOfIssuance: string // 签发国家\n  cityOfIssuance: string // 签发城市\n  provinceOfIssuance: string // 签发省份\n  issuanceDate: string // 签发日期\n  expirationDate: string // 到期日期\n  \n  // 丢失/被盗护照\n  hasLostPassport: boolean\n  lostPassportDetails?: LostPassportDetail[]\n}\n\nexport interface LostPassportDetail {\n  passportNumber: string\n  countryOfIssuance: string\n  explanation: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 3: 联系方式\n */\nexport interface Step3Data {\n  // 地址信息\n  homeAddress: Address\n  mailingAddress?: Address // 邮寄地址（如不同）\n  sameAsHomeAddress: boolean\n  \n  // 联系方式\n  primaryPhone: string\n  secondaryPhone?: string\n  workPhone?: string\n  email: string\n  \n  // 高风险：社交媒体\n  hasSocialMedia: boolean\n  socialMediaAccounts?: SocialMediaAccount[]\n}\n\nexport interface Address {\n  street: string\n  street2?: string\n  city: string\n  province: string\n  postalCode: string\n  country: string\n}\n\nexport interface SocialMediaAccount {\n  platform: string // Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn等\n  handle: string // 账号名\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 4: 旅行信息\n */\nexport interface Step4Data {\n  purposeOfTrip: TripPurpose\n  otherPurpose?: string\n  \n  // 行程细节\n  arrivalDate?: string\n  departureDate?: string\n  stayDuration?: number // 天数\n  specificTravelPlans: boolean\n  travelItinerary?: string\n  \n  // 地址信息\n  usAddress?: Address\n  \n  // 费用支付\n  whoPayingForTrip: 'self' | 'company' | 'other-person' | 'other-organization'\n  payerDetails?: PayerDetails\n  \n  // 高风险：是否有美国联系人\n  hasUSContact: boolean\n}\n\nexport type TripPurpose = \n  | 'tourism'\n  | 'business'\n  | 'study'\n  | 'work'\n  | 'transit'\n  | 'medical'\n  | 'other'\n\nexport interface PayerDetails {\n  name?: string\n  phone?: string\n  email?: string\n  relationship?: string\n  address?: Address\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n */\nexport interface Step5Data {\n  travelingWithOthers: boolean\n  groupTravel: boolean\n  groupName?: string\n  companions?: Companion[]\n}\n\nexport interface Companion {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  relationship: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 6: 美国联系人\n */\nexport interface Step6Data {\n  hasUSContact: boolean\n  contacts?: USContact[]\n}\n\nexport interface USContact {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  organizationName?: string\n  relationship: string\n  address: Address\n  phone: string\n  email?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 7: 家庭信息\n */\nexport interface Step7Data {\n  // 父亲信息\n  father: ParentInfo\n  \n  // 母亲信息\n  mother: ParentInfo\n  \n  // 配偶信息（如已婚）\n  hasSpouse: boolean\n  spouse?: SpouseInfo\n  \n  // 高风险：家庭成员在美情况\n  hasImmediateFamilyInUS: boolean\n  familyInUS?: FamilyMemberInUS[]\n}\n\nexport interface ParentInfo {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  dateOfBirth: string\n  countryOfBirth?: string\n  currentLocation?: string\n  isInUS: boolean\n}\n\nexport interface SpouseInfo {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  dateOfBirth: string\n  nationality: string\n  placeOfBirth: string\n  countryOfBirth: string\n  address: Address\n}\n\nexport interface FamilyMemberInUS {\n  relationship: string\n  name: string\n  status: 'us-citizen' | 'permanent-resident' | 'other'\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 8: 工作/教育\n */\nexport interface Step8Data {\n  currentOccupation: OccupationType\n  \n  // 当前工作/学校\n  employerOrSchool?: EmployerInfo\n  \n  // 高风险：过往雇主（最近5年）\n  hasPreviousEmployment: boolean\n  previousEmployers?: EmployerInfo[]\n  \n  // 教育背景\n  education?: EducationInfo[]\n  \n  // 专业技能\n  hasSpecializedSkills: boolean\n  specializedSkills?: string[]\n}\n\nexport type OccupationType = \n  | 'employed'\n  | 'self-employed'\n  | 'student'\n  | 'retired'\n  | 'unemployed'\n  | 'other'\n\nexport interface EmployerInfo {\n  name: string\n  address: Address\n  phone?: string\n  position: string\n  duties?: string\n  supervisorName?: string\n  supervisorPhone?: string\n  startDate: string\n  endDate?: string\n  monthlySalary?: number\n}\n\nexport interface EducationInfo {\n  institutionName: string\n  address: Address\n  attendanceFrom: string\n  attendanceTo: string\n  degree?: string\n  fieldOfStudy?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 9: 安全问题(1) - 全部高风险\n */\nexport interface Step9Data {\n  // 健康相关\n  hasCommunicableDisease: boolean\n  communicableDiseaseDetails?: string\n  \n  hasMentalDisorder: boolean\n  mentalDisorderDetails?: string\n  \n  isDrugAbuser: boolean\n  drugAbuseDetails?: string\n  \n  // 犯罪记录\n  hasBeenArrested: boolean\n  arrestDetails?: string\n  \n  hasViolatedDrugLaw: boolean\n  drugLawViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 道德问题\n  hasEngagedInProstitution: boolean\n  hasEngagedInHumanTrafficking: boolean\n  hasAssistedInHumanTrafficking: boolean\n  \n  // 洗钱/金融犯罪\n  hasEngagedInMoneyLaundering: boolean\n  moneyLaunderingDetails?: string\n  \n  // 儿童监护\n  hasCommittedChildAbduction: boolean\n  childAbductionDetails?: string\n  \n  // 投票违规\n  hasVotedInViolation: boolean\n  votingViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 公民身份\n  hasRenouncecitizenshipForTax: boolean\n  citizenshipRenunciationDetails?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 10: 安全问题(2) - 全部高风险\n */\nexport interface Step10Data {\n  // 恐怖主义\n  hasEngagedInTerrorism: boolean\n  terrorismDetails?: string\n  \n  hasSupportedTerrorism: boolean\n  terrorismSupportDetails?: string\n  \n  isTerroristOrgMember: boolean\n  terroristOrgDetails?: string\n  \n  // 种族灭绝/酷刑\n  hasCommittedGenocide: boolean\n  genocideDetails?: string\n  \n  hasCommittedTorture: boolean\n  tortureDetails?: string\n  \n  hasCommittedExtrajudicialKilling: boolean\n  killingDetails?: string\n  \n  // 宗教自由\n  hasViolatedReligiousFreedom: boolean\n  religiousFreedomDetails?: string\n  \n  // 强制人口控制\n  hasCoercedTransplantation: boolean\n  transplantationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 签证/移民违规\n  hasBeenDeported: boolean\n  deportationDetails?: string\n  \n  hasViolatedImmigrationLaw: boolean\n  immigrationViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  hasWithheldChildCustody: boolean\n  childCustodyDetails?: string\n  \n  // 签证欺诈\n  hasUsedFraudulentVisa: boolean\n  fraudulentVisaDetails?: string\n  \n  // 非法居留\n  hasOverstayed: boolean\n  overstayDetails?: string\n  \n  // 其他\n  hasBeenDeniedVisa: boolean\n  visaDenialDetails?: string\n  \n  hasBeenDeniedEntry: boolean\n  entryDenialDetails?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 11: 以往旅行\n */\nexport interface Step11Data {\n  // 过去5年访美记录\n  hasVisitedUS: boolean\n  usVisits?: USVisit[]\n  \n  // 过去5年其他国家旅行\n  hasInternationalTravel: boolean\n  internationalTravels?: InternationalTravel[]\n  \n  // 驾照信息\n  hasDriverLicense: boolean\n  driverLicenses?: DriverLicense[]\n}\n\nexport interface USVisit {\n  arrivalDate: string\n  lengthOfStay: number // 天数\n}\n\nexport interface InternationalTravel {\n  country: string\n  arrivalDate: string\n  lengthOfStay: number\n}\n\nexport interface DriverLicense {\n  licenseNumber: string\n  state: string\n  country: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n */\nexport interface Step12Data {\n  // 照片信息\n  photo?: PhotoInfo\n  \n  // 确认声明\n  confirmations: {\n    informationAccurate: boolean\n    understandPenalties: boolean\n    agreeToTerms: boolean\n  }\n  \n  // 签名\n  signature?: string\n  signatureDate?: string\n}\n\nexport interface PhotoInfo {\n  filename: string\n  uploadDate: string\n  size: number\n  mimeType: string\n  dataUrl?: string // Base64编码的图片数据\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 表单校验相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 字段校验规则\n */\nexport interface ValidationRule {\n  required?: boolean\n  pattern?: RegExp\n  minLength?: number\n  maxLength?: number\n  min?: number\n  max?: number\n  custom?: (value: any) => boolean | string\n}\n\n/**\n * 字段校验结果\n */\nexport interface ValidationResult {\n  valid: boolean\n  errors: string[]\n}\n\n/**\n * 步骤校验结果\n */\nexport interface StepValidation {\n  step: number\n  valid: boolean\n  errors: Record<string, string[]>\n  warnings: Record<string, string[]>\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// UI相关类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 步骤信息\n */\nexport interface StepInfo {\n  number: number\n  title: string\n  description: string\n  icon: string\n  completed: boolean\n  hasWarnings: boolean\n}\n\n/**\n * Toast通知类型\n */\nexport type ToastType = 'success' | 'error' | 'warning' | 'info'\n\nexport interface Toast {\n  id: string\n  type: ToastType\n  message: string\n  duration?: number\n}\n\n/**\n * Modal配置\n */\nexport interface ModalConfig {\n  title: string\n  message: string\n  confirmText?: string\n  cancelText?: string\n  type?: 'info' | 'warning' | 'danger'\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 套餐相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 套餐类型\n */\nexport type PlanType = 'free' | 'personal' | 'family'\n\n/**\n * 套餐信息\n */\nexport interface Plan {\n  id: PlanType\n  name: string\n  price: number\n  syncLimit: number | null // null表示无限制\n  features: string[]\n  popular?: boolean\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 同步相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 同步记录\n */\nexport interface SyncRecord {\n  id: string\n  draftId: string\n  timestamp: Date\n  success: boolean\n  errorMessage?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * 同步状态\n */\nexport interface SyncStatus {\n  syncing: boolean\n  lastSyncTime?: Date\n  error?: string\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第二批文件：布局和营销页面\n\n### 7. layouts/default.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\">\n    <!-- 顶部导航 -->\n    <header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\">\n      <nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center h-16\">\n          <!-- Logo -->\n          <NuxtLink to=\"/\" class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n            <Icon name=\"mdi:passport\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600\" />\n            <span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">DS-160 Helper</span>\n          </NuxtLink>\n\n          <!-- 桌面端导航 -->\n          <div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8\">\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/features\"\n              class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors\"\n            >\n              功能介绍\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/pricing\"\n              class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors\"\n            >\n              定价\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n              class=\"btn-primary\"\n            >\n              开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 移动端菜单按钮 -->\n          <button\n            @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = !mobileMenuOpen\"\n            class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100\"\n          >\n            <Icon\n              :name=\"mobileMenuOpen ? 'mdi:close' : 'mdi:menu'\"\n              class=\"w-6 h-6\"\n            />\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 移动端菜单 -->\n        <Transition\n          enter-active-class=\"transition duration-200 ease-out\"\n          enter-from-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n          enter-to-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n          leave-active-class=\"transition duration-100 ease-in\"\n          leave-from-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n          leave-to-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n        >\n          <div v-if=\"mobileMenuOpen\" class=\"md:hidden py-4 space-y-2\">\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/features\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              功能介绍\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/pricing\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              定价\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg text-center\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n        </Transition>\n      </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"flex-1\">\n      <slot />\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-300\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\">\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n          <!-- 公司信息 -->\n          <div class=\"col-span-1 md:col-span-2\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:passport\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-400\" />\n              <span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">DS-160 Helper</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4\">\n              简化DS-160表单填写流程，让签证申请更轻松。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">\n              © 2024 DS-160 Helper. All rights reserved.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 产品 -->\n          <div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">产品</h3>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/features\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  功能介绍\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/pricing\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  定价方案\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/app/dashboard\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  开始使用\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 支持 -->\n          <div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">支持</h3>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">帮助中心</a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">隐私政策</a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">服务条款</a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nconst mobileMenuOpen = ref(false)\n\n// 关闭移动菜单（路由变化时）\nconst route = useRoute()\nwatch(() => route.path, () => {\n  mobileMenuOpen.value = false\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 8. layouts/app.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\">\n    <!-- 顶部导航栏 -->\n    <AppHeader />\n\n    <div class=\"flex\">\n      <!-- 左侧步骤导航 -->\n      <aside\n        class=\"hidden lg:block w-64 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] sticky top-16\"\n      >\n        <StepNavigation />\n      </aside>\n\n      <!-- 主内容区域 -->\n      <main class=\"flex-1 p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n          <slot />\n        </div>\n      </main>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 移动端步骤导航（底部） -->\n    <div class=\"lg:hidden fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white border-t border-gray-200 z-40\">\n      <MobileStepNavigation />\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Toast通知 -->\n    <ToastContainer />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\n// 确保在应用布局中初始化必要的stores\nconst draftStore = useDraftStore()\nconst formStore = useFormStore()\n\n// 页面加载时初始化\nonMounted(() => {\n  draftStore.loadDrafts()\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 9. pages/index.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <!-- Hero Section -->\n    <section class=\"relative bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 text-white overflow-hidden\">\n      <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-grid-white/[0.05] bg-[size:20px_20px]\" />\n      <div class=\"relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28\">\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\n          <h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in\">\n            DS-160 表单填写\n            <br />\n            <span class=\"text-primary-200\">从未如此简单</span>\n          </h1>\n          <p class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up\">\n            智能引导 · 高风险提示 · 自动保存草稿\n            <br />\n            让美国签证申请不再令人头疼\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-slide-up\">\n            <NuxtLink to=\"/app/dashboard\" class=\"btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:rocket-launch\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n              免费开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink to=\"/features\" class=\"btn bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:information\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n              了解更多\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 核心卖点 -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-white\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n            为什么选择 DS-160 Helper？\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n            专为中国申请者设计，解决DS-160表单填写的所有痛点\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:list-box-outline\"\n            title=\"12步智能引导\"\n            description=\"复杂表单拆解为清晰步骤，每步都有中文说明和填写建议\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:alert-circle\"\n            title=\"高风险字段提示\"\n            description=\"自动识别敏感问题，橙色警告框+专业建议，避免拒签风险\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:content-save-outline\"\n            title=\"自动保存草稿\"\n            description=\"实时保存到本地，随时暂停随时继续，永不丢失数据\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:sync\"\n            title=\"一键同步DS-160\"\n            description=\"填写完成后，一键同步到官方网站，节省80%时间\"\n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 工作流程 -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-gray-50\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n            三步完成DS-160\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600\">\n            简单、快速、安全\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n          <ProcessStep\n            number=\"1\"\n            title=\"创建草稿\"\n            description=\"点击开始，创建您的DS-160草稿，所有数据本地保存\"\n            icon=\"mdi:file-document-edit-outline\"\n          />\n          <ProcessStep\n            number=\"2\"\n            title=\"填写表单\"\n            description=\"按照12个步骤填写，每个字段都有详细说明和示例\"\n            icon=\"mdi:form-textbox\"\n          />\n          <ProcessStep\n            number=\"3\"\n            title=\"同步提交\"\n            description=\"检查确认后，一键同步到DS-160官网，完成申请\"\n            icon=\"mdi:cloud-upload-outline\"\n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 用户评价 -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-white\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n            用户真实反馈\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600\">\n            已帮助 10,000+ 用户成功填写DS-160\n          \n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: QAEngineer\n\nProcess still running."}],"details":{"status":"running","sessionId":"young-river","aggregated":"/home/gem/.local/lib/python3.12/site-packages/flaml/__init__.py:20: UserWarning: flaml.automl is not available. Please install flaml[automl] to enable AutoML functionalities.\n  warnings.warn(\"flaml.automl is not available. Please install flaml[automl] to enable AutoML functionalities.\")\n================================================================================\n🚀 DS-160 Helper MVP开发 - AG2团队启动\n================================================================================\n\n项目需求：\n\n开发 DS-160 Helper MVP - 美国签证DS-160申请表辅助填写工具\n\n【技术栈】\n- 框架：Nuxt 3 + Vue 3 + TypeScript\n- 样式：Tailwind CSS v4\n- 状态管理：Pinia\n- 构建：Vite 8\n\n【核心功能】\n1. 营销页面（SSR）\n   - 首页（/）：产品介绍、核心卖点\n   - 功能介绍（/features）：12步引导、高风险提示等\n   - 定价页（/pricing）：免费版/个人版/家庭版对比\n\n2. 应用页面（CSR，/app/*）\n   - 用户面板（/app/dashboard）：草稿列表\n   - 表单填写（/app/form/step-[1-12]）：12个步骤的表单\n     * Step 1: 个人信息\n     * Step 2: 护照信息\n     * Step 3: 联系方式\n     * Step 4: 旅行信息\n     * Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n     * Step 6: 美国联系人\n     * Step 7: 家庭信息\n     * Step 8: 工作/教育\n     * Step 9: 安全问题(1)\n     * Step 10: 安全问题(2)\n     * Step 11: 以往旅行\n     * Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n   - 草稿管理（/app/drafts）：查看和恢复草稿\n\n3. 关键特性\n   - 草稿自动保存到localStorage\n   - 每个字段有中文说明和填写建议\n   - 高风险字段用橙色警告框标注\n   - 实时表单校验\n   - 进度追踪（已完成X/12步）\n   - 模拟同步功能（计数，剩余X次）\n   - 响应式设计（移动端友好）\n\n【路由配置】\n- SSR页面：/, /features, /pricing\n- CSR页面：/app/**\n\n【数据结构】\nDraft接口：\n- id: string\n- createdAt: Date\n- updatedAt: Date\n- currentStep: number (1-12)\n- syncCount: number (已使用的同步次数，免费版限3次)\n- data: object (各步骤的表单数据)\n\n【UI要求】\n- 简洁现代的设计风格\n- 使用Tailwind CSS v4\n- 高风险字段：橙色边框 + 警告图标 + 提示文字\n- 步骤导航：左侧边栏，显示进度\n- 移动端：响应式布局，适配小屏幕\n\n【MVP范围】\n✅ 包含：营销页、表单填写、草稿管理、模拟同步\n❌ 不包含：真实登录、后端API、支付、Chrome插件、真实DS-160同步\n\n请生成完整可运行的Nuxt 3项目代码。\n\n\n================================================================================\nUser (to chat_manager):\n\n\n【项目需求】\n\n开发 DS-160 Helper MVP - 美国签证DS-160申请表辅助填写工具\n\n【技术栈】\n- 框架：Nuxt 3 + Vue 3 + TypeScript\n- 样式：Tailwind CSS v4\n- 状态管理：Pinia\n- 构建：Vite 8\n\n【核心功能】\n1. 营销页面（SSR）\n   - 首页（/）：产品介绍、核心卖点\n   - 功能介绍（/features）：12步引导、高风险提示等\n   - 定价页（/pricing）：免费版/个人版/家庭版对比\n\n2. 应用页面（CSR，/app/*）\n   - 用户面板（/app/dashboard）：草稿列表\n   - 表单填写（/app/form/step-[1-12]）：12个步骤的表单\n     * Step 1: 个人信息\n     * Step 2: 护照信息\n     * Step 3: 联系方式\n     * Step 4: 旅行信息\n     * Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n     * Step 6: 美国联系人\n     * Step 7: 家庭信息\n     * Step 8: 工作/教育\n     * Step 9: 安全问题(1)\n     * Step 10: 安全问题(2)\n     * Step 11: 以往旅行\n     * Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n   - 草稿管理（/app/drafts）：查看和恢复草稿\n\n3. 关键特性\n   - 草稿自动保存到localStorage\n   - 每个字段有中文说明和填写建议\n   - 高风险字段用橙色警告框标注\n   - 实时表单校验\n   - 进度追踪（已完成X/12步）\n   - 模拟同步功能（计数，剩余X次）\n   - 响应式设计（移动端友好）\n\n【路由配置】\n- SSR页面：/, /features, /pricing\n- CSR页面：/app/**\n\n【数据结构】\nDraft接口：\n- id: string\n- createdAt: Date\n- updatedAt: Date\n- currentStep: number (1-12)\n- syncCount: number (已使用的同步次数，免费版限3次)\n- data: object (各步骤的表单数据)\n\n【UI要求】\n- 简洁现代的设计风格\n- 使用Tailwind CSS v4\n- 高风险字段：橙色边框 + 警告图标 + 提示文字\n- 步骤导航：左侧边栏，显示进度\n- 移动端：响应式布局，适配小屏幕\n\n【MVP范围】\n✅ 包含：营销页、表单填写、草稿管理、模拟同步\n❌ 不包含：真实登录、后端API、支付、Chrome插件、真实DS-160同步\n\n请生成完整可运行的Nuxt 3项目代码。\n\n\n【开发流程】\n1. Product Manager: 分析需求，拆解任务\n2. Frontend Developer: 开发完整的Nuxt 3应用\n3. QA Engineer: 代码审查和功能检查\n4. DevOps Engineer: 部署文档和运行说明\n\n请按顺序开始工作。Product Manager先进行需求分析和任务拆解。\n\n【重要】Frontend Developer必须生成完整可运行的代码文件，包括：\n- package.json\n- nuxt.config.ts\n- 所有页面文件（pages/）\n- 所有组件文件（components/）\n- Pinia stores（stores/）\n- README.md\n\n代码必须写入到 outputs/ds160-helper/ 目录。\n\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: ProductManager\n\n[33m[autogen.oai.client: 04-11 00:05:39] {329} WARNING - Model us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0 is not found. The cost will be 0. In your config_list, add field {\"price\" : [prompt_price_per_1k, completion_token_price_per_1k]} for customized pricing.[0m\nProductManager (to chat_manager):\n\n# DS-160 Helper MVP - 需求分析与任务拆解\n\n## 一、需求分析\n\n### 1.1 项目概述\n开发一个美国签证DS-160申请表辅助填写工具的MVP版本，帮助用户更便捷地准备和填写DS-160表单。\n\n### 1.2 用户价值\n- **简化流程**：将复杂的DS-160表单拆解为12个清晰步骤\n- **降低风险**：高风险字段提供明确警告和填写建议\n- **数据保护**：本地草稿保存，避免数据丢失\n- **提高效率**：中文说明和实时校验减少错误\n\n### 1.3 技术架构分析\n```\n技术栈：\n├── Nuxt 3 (SSR/CSR混合渲染)\n├── Vue 3 + TypeScript (类型安全)\n├── Tailwind CSS v4 (现代样式)\n├── Pinia (状态管理)\n└── Vite 8 (快速构建)\n\n渲染策略：\n├── SSR: 营销页面（SEO优化）\n└── CSR: 应用页面（交互体验）\n```\n\n### 1.4 核心挑战\n1. **数据持久化**：localStorage管理复杂表单数据\n2. **表单校验**：12步骤的联动校验逻辑\n3. **用户体验**：步骤导航、进度追踪、响应式设计\n4. **风险提示**：高风险字段的识别和展示\n\n---\n\n## 二、功能清单（分模块）\n\n### 模块A：项目基础架构\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0（最高）**\n\n- [ ] A1: 初始化Nuxt 3项目\n- [ ] A2: 配置TypeScript\n- [ ] A3: 配置Tailwind CSS v4\n- [ ] A4: 配置Pinia状态管理\n- [ ] A5: 配置路由（SSR/CSR分离）\n- [ ] A6: 创建基础布局组件\n\n**产出物：**\n```\noutputs/ds160-helper/\n├── package.json\n├── nuxt.config.ts\n├── tsconfig.json\n├── tailwind.config.js\n└── layouts/\n    ├── default.vue\n    └── app.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块B：营销页面（SSR）\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P1**\n\n#### B1: 首页 (/)\n- [ ] Hero Section（产品介绍）\n- [ ] 核心卖点展示（3-4个亮点）\n- [ ] CTA按钮（开始使用）\n- [ ] 响应式设计\n\n#### B2: 功能介绍页 (/features)\n- [ ] 12步引导流程展示\n- [ ] 高风险提示功能说明\n- [ ] 草稿自动保存说明\n- [ ] 特性列表卡片\n\n#### B3: 定价页 (/pricing)\n- [ ] 三种套餐对比表格\n  - 免费版：3次同步\n  - 个人版：无限同步\n  - 家庭版：5个账号\n- [ ] 功能对比清单\n- [ ] CTA按钮\n\n**产出物：**\n```\npages/\n├── index.vue\n├── features.vue\n└── pricing.vue\n\ncomponents/marketing/\n├── HeroSection.vue\n├── FeatureCard.vue\n├── PricingCard.vue\n└── CTAButton.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块C：应用页面 - 基础框架\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0**\n\n#### C1: 应用布局\n- [ ] 顶部导航栏（Logo、用户菜单）\n- [ ] 左侧步骤导航（12步骤列表）\n- [ ] 主内容区域\n- [ ] 进度指示器（X/12完成）\n- [ ] 移动端响应式侧边栏\n\n#### C2: 用户面板 (/app/dashboard)\n- [ ] 欢迎信息\n- [ ] 草稿列表展示\n- [ ] 创建新草稿按钮\n- [ ] 继续填写按钮\n- [ ] 删除草稿功能\n\n#### C3: 草稿管理 (/app/drafts)\n- [ ] 草稿列表（表格视图）\n- [ ] 草稿信息（创建时间、更新时间、当前步骤）\n- [ ] 操作按钮（编辑、删除、导出）\n- [ ] 空状态提示\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nlayouts/\n└── app.vue\n\npages/app/\n├── dashboard.vue\n└── drafts.vue\n\ncomponents/app/\n├── AppHeader.vue\n├── StepNavigation.vue\n├── ProgressBar.vue\n└── DraftCard.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块D：表单填写 - 核心功能\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0**\n\n#### D1: 表单通用组件\n- [ ] FormInput（文本输入）\n- [ ] FormSelect（下拉选择）\n- [ ] FormDatePicker（日期选择）\n- [ ] FormRadio（单选）\n- [ ] FormCheckbox（多选）\n- [ ] WarningField（高风险字段包装器）\n- [ ] FieldHelper（帮助提示）\n\n#### D2: 表单校验系统\n- [ ] 实时校验逻辑\n- [ ] 错误提示展示\n- [ ] 必填字段标记\n- [ ] 步骤完成度检查\n\n#### D3: 12个步骤页面\n- [ ] Step 1: 个人信息\n  - 姓名（中英文）\n  - 性别\n  - 出生日期、地点\n  - **高风险**：曾用名、别名\n  \n- [ ] Step 2: 护照信息\n  - 护照号码\n  - 签发日期、到期日期\n  - 签发地点\n  \n- [ ] Step 3: 联系方式\n  - 电话、邮箱\n  - 地址（中英文）\n  - **高风险**：社交媒体账号\n  \n- [ ] Step 4: 旅行信息\n  - 旅行目的\n  - 预计停留时间\n  - 费用支付人\n  - **高风险**：是否有美国联系人\n  \n- [ ] Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n  - 是否同行\n  - 同行人信息\n  \n- [ ] Step 6: 美国联系人\n  - 联系人姓名、关系\n  - 联系方式、地址\n  \n- [ ] Step 7: 家庭信息\n  - 父母信息\n  - 配偶信息（如适用）\n  - **高风险**：家庭成员在美情况\n  \n- [ ] Step 8: 工作/教育\n  - 当前职业/学校\n  - 工作单位/学校地址\n  - 收入情况\n  - **高风险**：过往雇主信息\n  \n- [ ] Step 9: 安全问题(1)\n  - **全部高风险**\n  - 传染病史\n  - 犯罪记录\n  - 恐怖组织关联\n  \n- [ ] Step 10: 安全问题(2)\n  - **全部高风险**\n  - 签证拒签史\n  - 非法滞留史\n  - 儿童监护权问题\n  \n- [ ] Step 11: 以往旅行\n  - 过去5年访美记录\n  - 其他国家旅行记录\n  \n- [ ] Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n  - 照片上传（模拟）\n  - 信息确认清单\n  - 提交前检查\n\n**产出物：**\n```\npages/app/form/\n├── step-1.vue\n├── step-2.vue\n├── step-3.vue\n├── step-4.vue\n├── step-5.vue\n├── step-6.vue\n├── step-7.vue\n├── step-8.vue\n├── step-9.vue\n├── step-10.vue\n├── step-11.vue\n└── step-12.vue\n\ncomponents/form/\n├── FormInput.vue\n├── FormSelect.vue\n├── FormDatePicker.vue\n├── FormRadio.vue\n├── FormCheckbox.vue\n├── WarningField.vue\n├── FieldHelper.vue\n└── StepActions.vue (上一步/下一步按钮)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块E：状态管理（Pinia）\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0**\n\n#### E1: Draft Store\n- [ ] 草稿CRUD操作\n- [ ] 当前草稿状态管理\n- [ ] localStorage持久化\n- [ ] 自动保存逻辑（防抖）\n\n#### E2: Form Store\n- [ ] 当前步骤管理\n- [ ] 表单数据管理\n- [ ] 校验状态管理\n- [ ] 步骤完成度计算\n\n#### E3: Sync Store\n- [ ] 同步次数计数\n- [ ] 模拟同步功能\n- [ ] 套餐限制检查\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nstores/\n├── draft.ts\n├── form.ts\n└── sync.ts\n\ntypes/\n└── index.ts (Draft、FormData等接口定义)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块F：UI组件库\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P1**\n\n#### F1: 通用组件\n- [ ] Button（主要、次要、危险）\n- [ ] Card\n- [ ] Modal\n- [ ] Toast通知\n- [ ] Loading状态\n\n#### F2: 特殊组件\n- [ ] WarningBox（橙色警告框）\n- [ ] ProgressIndicator\n- [ ] StepBadge（步骤徽章）\n\n**产出物：**\n```\ncomponents/ui/\n├── Button.vue\n├── Card.vue\n├── Modal.vue\n├── Toast.vue\n├── Loading.vue\n├── WarningBox.vue\n├── ProgressIndicator.vue\n└── StepBadge.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块G：工具函数\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P1**\n\n- [ ] G1: 表单校验工具\n- [ ] G2: 日期格式化\n- [ ] G3: localStorage操作封装\n- [ ] G4: 防抖/节流函数\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nutils/\n├── validation.ts\n├── date.ts\n├── storage.ts\n└── helpers.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块H：文档与配置\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P2**\n\n- [ ] H1: README.md（项目说明、安装运行）\n- [ ] H2: 开发文档（项目结构、开发规范）\n- [ ] H3: 部署文档（构建、部署步骤）\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nREADME.md\ndocs/\n├── DEVELOPMENT.md\n└── DEPLOYMENT.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、开发计划\n\n### 阶段1：基础架构（第1天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块A（项目基础架构）\n产出：可运行的Nuxt 3项目骨架\n```\n\n### 阶段2：营销页面（第1-2天）\n```\n时间：6小时\n任务：模块B（营销页面）\n产出：3个营销页面（SSR渲染）\n```\n\n### 阶段3：应用框架（第2天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块C（应用页面基础框架）\n产出：应用布局、Dashboard、草稿管理\n```\n\n### 阶段4：核心表单（第3-5天）\n```\n时间：16小时\n任务：模块D（表单填写）+ 模块E（状态管理）\n产出：12个步骤页面 + Pinia stores\n```\n\n### 阶段5：UI组件（第5天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块F（UI组件库）+ 模块G（工具函数）\n产出：通用组件库 + 工具函数\n```\n\n### 阶段6：文档与测试（第6天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块H（文档）+ QA测试\n产出：完整文档 + 测试报告\n```\n\n**总计：38小时（约6个工作日）**\n\n---\n\n## 四、里程碑\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 1: 项目启动（Day 1）\n**目标：** 完成基础架构和营销页面\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ Nuxt 3项目可运行\n- ✅ Tailwind CSS配置完成\n- ✅ 3个营销页面上线\n\n**验收标准：**\n- `npm run dev` 可正常启动\n- 访问 `/`, `/features`, `/pricing` 正常渲染\n- 响应式设计在移动端正常显示\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 2: 应用框架（Day 2）\n**目标：** 完成应用页面框架\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 应用布局（侧边栏导航）\n- ✅ Dashboard页面\n- ✅ 草稿管理页面\n- ✅ Pinia stores基础结构\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 可以创建新草稿\n- 草稿列表正常显示\n- localStorage保存/读取正常\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 3: 核心表单（Day 3-5）\n**目标：** 完成12步表单填写\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 12个步骤页面\n- ✅ 表单组件库\n- ✅ 实时校验功能\n- ✅ 高风险字段警告\n- ✅ 自动保存功能\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 可以完整走完12个步骤\n- 表单数据正确保存到localStorage\n- 高风险字段显示橙色警告\n- 步骤导航显示进度\n- 实时校验提示错误\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 4: MVP完成（Day 6）\n**目标：** 完整可用的MVP版本\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 所有功能模块\n- ✅ UI组件库\n- ✅ 完整文档\n- ✅ QA测试通过\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 用户可以从头到尾完成表单填写\n- 草稿管理功能正常\n- 模拟同步功能正常（计数）\n- 移动端体验良好\n- 代码质量检查通过\n- README文档完整\n\n---\n\n## 五、技术规范\n\n### 5.1 代码规范\n```typescript\n// 文件命名：kebab-case\n// 组件命名：PascalCase\n// 函数命名：camelCase\n// 常量命名：UPPER_SNAKE_CASE\n\n// TypeScript严格模式\n// ESLint + Prettier\n```\n\n### 5.2 Git提交规范\n```\nfeat: 新功能\nfix: 修复bug\ndocs: 文档更新\nstyle: 代码格式调整\nrefactor: 重构\ntest: 测试\nchore: 构建/工具链\n```\n\n### 5.3 目录结构\n```\noutputs/ds160-helper/\n├── .nuxt/                  # Nuxt构建缓存\n├── components/             # Vue组件\n│   ├── app/               # 应用组件\n│   ├── form/              # 表单组件\n│   ├── marketing/         # 营销组件\n│   └── ui/                # UI组件库\n├── layouts/               # 布局\n├── pages/                 # 路由页面\n│   ├── app/              # 应用页面（CSR）\n│   └── *.vue             # 营销页面（SSR）\n├── stores/                # Pinia状态管理\n├── types/                 # TypeScript类型定义\n├── utils/                 # 工具函数\n├── public/                # 静态资源\n├── nuxt.config.ts         # Nuxt配置\n├── tailwind.config.js     # Tailwind配置\n├── package.json           # 依赖配置\n└── README.md              # 项目文档\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、风险评估\n\n### 高风险项\n1. **localStorage容量限制**\n   - 风险：表单数据可能超过5MB限制\n   - 缓解：数据压缩、分块存储\n\n2. **表单校验复杂度**\n   - 风险：12步骤联动校验逻辑复杂\n   - 缓解：模块化校验、单元测试\n\n3. **移动端体验**\n   - 风险：复杂表单在小屏幕上难用\n   - 缓解：响应式设计、渐进式展示\n\n### 中风险项\n1. **浏览器兼容性**\n   - 风险：部分API不兼容旧浏览器\n   - 缓解：Polyfill、浏览器检测\n\n2. **性能优化**\n   - 风险：大量表单字段影响性能\n   - 缓解：虚拟滚动、懒加载\n\n---\n\n## 七、下一步行动\n\n### 👨💻 Frontend Developer\n**现在开始开发！**\n\n请按以下顺序生成代码：\n\n1. **第一批文件（基础架构）**\n   - package.json\n   - nuxt.config.ts\n   - tsconfig.json\n   - tailwind.config.js\n   - types/index.ts\n\n2. **第二批文件（布局和营销页面）**\n   - layouts/default.vue\n   - layouts/app.vue\n   - pages/index.vue\n   - pages/features.vue\n   - pages/pricing.vue\n\n3. **第三批文件（应用页面）**\n   - pages/app/dashboard.vue\n   - pages/app/drafts.vue\n   - components/app/*\n\n4. **第四批文件（表单系统）**\n   - pages/app/form/step-*.vue\n   - components/form/*\n   - stores/*\n\n5. **第五批文件（UI组件和工具）**\n   - components/ui/*\n   - utils/*\n\n6. **第六批文件（文档）**\n   - README.md\n   - docs/*\n\n---\n\n**所有代码必须写入 `outputs/ds160-helper/` 目录**\n\n开始开发吧！💪\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: FrontendDeveloper\n\n[33m[autogen.oai.client: 04-11 00:07:36] {329} WARNING - Model us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0 is not found. The cost will be 0. In your config_list, add field {\"price\" : [prompt_price_per_1k, completion_token_price_per_1k]} for customized pricing.[0m\nFrontendDeveloper (to chat_manager):\n\n# Frontend Developer - 开始开发 DS-160 Helper MVP\n\n我将按照Product Manager的规划，逐步生成完整的Nuxt 3项目代码。\n\n---\n\n## 第一批文件：基础架构\n\n### 1. package.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"ds160-helper\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"DS-160 Helper MVP - 美国签证申请表辅助填写工具\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"nuxt dev\",\n    \"build\": \"nuxt build\",\n    \"generate\": \"nuxt generate\",\n    \"preview\": \"nuxt preview\",\n    \"postinstall\": \"nuxt prepare\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"nuxt typecheck\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@nuxt/icon\": \"^1.0.0\",\n    \"@pinia/nuxt\": \"^0.5.1\",\n    \"nuxt\": \"^3.11.2\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^2.1.7\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.4.21\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.3.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@nuxt/eslint-config\": \"^0.3.0\",\n    \"@nuxtjs/tailwindcss\": \"^6.12.0\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^20.12.7\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.57.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.5\",\n    \"vue-tsc\": \"^2.0.13\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. nuxt.config.ts\n\n```typescript\n// https://nuxt.com/docs/api/configuration/nuxt-config\nexport default defineNuxtConfig({\n  devtools: { enabled: true },\n  \n  modules: [\n    '@nuxtjs/tailwindcss',\n    '@pinia/nuxt',\n    '@nuxt/icon'\n  ],\n\n  // TypeScript配置\n  typescript: {\n    strict: true,\n    typeCheck: true\n  },\n\n  // 路由配置：SSR/CSR分离\n  routeRules: {\n    // 营销页面使用SSR\n    '/': { ssr: true },\n    '/features': { ssr: true },\n    '/pricing': { ssr: true },\n    \n    // 应用页面使用CSR\n    '/app/**': { ssr: false }\n  },\n\n  // App配置\n  app: {\n    head: {\n      title: 'DS-160 Helper - 美国签证申请表辅助工具',\n      meta: [\n        { charset: 'utf-8' },\n        { name: 'viewport', content: 'width=device-width, initial-scale=1' },\n        { \n          name: 'description', \n          content: '简化DS-160表单填写流程，智能提示高风险字段，自动保存草稿，让签证申请更轻松' \n        }\n      ],\n      link: [\n        { rel: 'icon', type: 'image/x-icon', href: '/favicon.ico' }\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n\n  // CSS配置\n  css: [\n    '~/assets/css/main.css'\n  ],\n\n  // Tailwind CSS配置\n  tailwindcss: {\n    cssPath: '~/assets/css/main.css',\n    configPath: 'tailwind.config.js',\n    exposeConfig: false,\n    viewer: true\n  },\n\n  // 构建配置\n  vite: {\n    vue: {\n      script: {\n        defineModel: true,\n        propsDestructure: true\n      }\n    }\n  },\n\n  // 兼容性日期\n  compatibilityDate: '2024-04-03'\n})\n```\n\n### 3. tsconfig.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"./.nuxt/tsconfig.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"noUnusedLocals\": true,\n    \"noUnusedParameters\": true,\n    \"noImplicitReturns\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"bundler\",\n    \"resolveJsonModule\": true,\n    \"allowSyntheticDefaultImports\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"types\": [\n      \"node\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"include\": [\n    \"**/*\",\n    \".nuxt/**/*\"\n  ],\n  \"exclude\": [\n    \"node_modules\",\n    \".nuxt\",\n    \"dist\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 4. tailwind.config.js\n\n```javascript\n/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */\nexport default {\n  content: [\n    \"./components/**/*.{js,vue,ts}\",\n    \"./layouts/**/*.vue\",\n    \"./pages/**/*.vue\",\n    \"./plugins/**/*.{js,ts}\",\n    \"./app.vue\",\n    \"./error.vue\",\n  ],\n  theme: {\n    extend: {\n      colors: {\n        primary: {\n          50: '#eff6ff',\n          100: '#dbeafe',\n          200: '#bfdbfe',\n          300: '#93c5fd',\n          400: '#60a5fa',\n          500: '#3b82f6',\n          600: '#2563eb',\n          700: '#1d4ed8',\n          800: '#1e40af',\n          900: '#1e3a8a',\n          950: '#172554',\n        },\n        warning: {\n          50: '#fff7ed',\n          100: '#ffedd5',\n          200: '#fed7aa',\n          300: '#fdba74',\n          400: '#fb923c',\n          500: '#f97316',\n          600: '#ea580c',\n          700: '#c2410c',\n          800: '#9a3412',\n          900: '#7c2d12',\n          950: '#431407',\n        }\n      },\n      fontFamily: {\n        sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],\n      },\n      animation: {\n        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out',\n        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.3s ease-out',\n        'slide-down': 'slideDown 0.3s ease-out',\n      },\n      keyframes: {\n        fadeIn: {\n          '0%': { opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { opacity: '1' },\n        },\n        slideUp: {\n          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(10px)', opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },\n        },\n        slideDown: {\n          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(-10px)', opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n  plugins: [],\n}\n```\n\n### 5. assets/css/main.css\n\n```css\n@tailwind base;\n@tailwind components;\n@tailwind utilities;\n\n@layer base {\n  * {\n    @apply border-border;\n  }\n  \n  body {\n    @apply bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 antialiased;\n  }\n\n  h1 {\n    @apply text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h2 {\n    @apply text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h3 {\n    @apply text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h4 {\n    @apply text-xl font-semibold;\n  }\n}\n\n@layer components {\n  /* 自定义滚动条 */\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n    @apply w-2;\n  }\n\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n    @apply bg-gray-100;\n  }\n\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n    @apply bg-gray-300 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-400;\n  }\n\n  /* 表单输入通用样式 */\n  .form-input {\n    @apply w-full px-4 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg \n           focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 \n           transition-colors duration-200 outline-none;\n  }\n\n  .form-input-error {\n    @apply border-red-500 focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500;\n  }\n\n  .form-input-warning {\n    @apply border-warning-500 focus:ring-warning-500 focus:border-warning-500;\n  }\n\n  /* 按钮基础样式 */\n  .btn {\n    @apply px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200 \n           focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 \n           disabled:cursor-not-allowed;\n  }\n\n  .btn-primary {\n    @apply btn bg-primary-600 text-white hover:bg-primary-700 \n           focus:ring-primary-500 active:bg-primary-800;\n  }\n\n  .btn-secondary {\n    @apply btn bg-gray-200 text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-300 \n           focus:ring-gray-500;\n  }\n\n  .btn-danger {\n    @apply btn bg-red-600 text-white hover:bg-red-700 \n           focus:ring-red-500;\n  }\n\n  .btn-outline {\n    @apply btn border-2 border-primary-600 text-primary-600 \n           hover:bg-primary-50 focus:ring-primary-500;\n  }\n}\n\n@layer utilities {\n  .text-balance {\n    text-wrap: balance;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 6. types/index.ts\n\n```typescript\n/**\n * DS-160 Helper - TypeScript类型定义\n */\n\n// ============================================\n// 草稿相关类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 草稿状态\n */\nexport type DraftStatus = 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'archived'\n\n/**\n * 草稿接口\n */\nexport interface Draft {\n  id: string\n  createdAt: Date\n  updatedAt: Date\n  currentStep: number // 1-12\n  status: DraftStatus\n  syncCount: number // 已使用的同步次数\n  data: FormData\n}\n\n/**\n * 创建草稿的输入参数\n */\nexport interface CreateDraftInput {\n  data?: Partial<FormData>\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 表单数据类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 完整表单数据\n */\nexport interface FormData {\n  step1?: Step1Data\n  step2?: Step2Data\n  step3?: Step3Data\n  step4?: Step4Data\n  step5?: Step5Data\n  step6?: Step6Data\n  step7?: Step7Data\n  step8?: Step8Data\n  step9?: Step9Data\n  step10?: Step10Data\n  step11?: Step11Data\n  step12?: Step12Data\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 1: 个人信息\n */\nexport interface Step1Data {\n  // 基本信息\n  surname: string // 姓（拼音）\n  givenName: string // 名（拼音）\n  surnameZh?: string // 姓（中文）\n  givenNameZh?: string // 名（中文）\n  fullNameNative?: string // 母语全名\n  \n  // 高风险字段\n  hasOtherNames: boolean // 是否有曾用名/别名\n  otherNames?: OtherName[] // 曾用名列表\n  \n  // 其他信息\n  gender: 'M' | 'F' | 'X' // 性别\n  maritalStatus: 'single' | 'married' | 'divorced' | 'widowed' | 'separated' // 婚姻状态\n  dateOfBirth: string // 出生日期 YYYY-MM-DD\n  cityOfBirth: string // 出生城市\n  provinceOfBirth: string // 出生省份\n  countryOfBirth: string // 出生国家\n  nationality: string // 国籍\n}\n\nexport interface OtherName {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  type: 'maiden' | 'previous' | 'alias' // 娘家姓/曾用名/别名\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 2: 护照信息\n */\nexport interface Step2Data {\n  passportNumber: string // 护照号码\n  passportBookNumber?: string // 护照本编号（如有）\n  countryOfIssuance: string // 签发国家\n  cityOfIssuance: string // 签发城市\n  provinceOfIssuance: string // 签发省份\n  issuanceDate: string // 签发日期\n  expirationDate: string // 到期日期\n  \n  // 丢失/被盗护照\n  hasLostPassport: boolean\n  lostPassportDetails?: LostPassportDetail[]\n}\n\nexport interface LostPassportDetail {\n  passportNumber: string\n  countryOfIssuance: string\n  explanation: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 3: 联系方式\n */\nexport interface Step3Data {\n  // 地址信息\n  homeAddress: Address\n  mailingAddress?: Address // 邮寄地址（如不同）\n  sameAsHomeAddress: boolean\n  \n  // 联系方式\n  primaryPhone: string\n  secondaryPhone?: string\n  workPhone?: string\n  email: string\n  \n  // 高风险：社交媒体\n  hasSocialMedia: boolean\n  socialMediaAccounts?: SocialMediaAccount[]\n}\n\nexport interface Address {\n  street: string\n  street2?: string\n  city: string\n  province: string\n  postalCode: string\n  country: string\n}\n\nexport interface SocialMediaAccount {\n  platform: string // Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn等\n  handle: string // 账号名\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 4: 旅行信息\n */\nexport interface Step4Data {\n  purposeOfTrip: TripPurpose\n  otherPurpose?: string\n  \n  // 行程细节\n  arrivalDate?: string\n  departureDate?: string\n  stayDuration?: number // 天数\n  specificTravelPlans: boolean\n  travelItinerary?: string\n  \n  // 地址信息\n  usAddress?: Address\n  \n  // 费用支付\n  whoPayingForTrip: 'self' | 'company' | 'other-person' | 'other-organization'\n  payerDetails?: PayerDetails\n  \n  // 高风险：是否有美国联系人\n  hasUSContact: boolean\n}\n\nexport type TripPurpose = \n  | 'tourism'\n  | 'business'\n  | 'study'\n  | 'work'\n  | 'transit'\n  | 'medical'\n  | 'other'\n\nexport interface PayerDetails {\n  name?: string\n  phone?: string\n  email?: string\n  relationship?: string\n  address?: Address\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n */\nexport interface Step5Data {\n  travelingWithOthers: boolean\n  groupTravel: boolean\n  groupName?: string\n  companions?: Companion[]\n}\n\nexport interface Companion {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  relationship: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 6: 美国联系人\n */\nexport interface Step6Data {\n  hasUSContact: boolean\n  contacts?: USContact[]\n}\n\nexport interface USContact {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  organizationName?: string\n  relationship: string\n  address: Address\n  phone: string\n  email?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 7: 家庭信息\n */\nexport interface Step7Data {\n  // 父亲信息\n  father: ParentInfo\n  \n  // 母亲信息\n  mother: ParentInfo\n  \n  // 配偶信息（如已婚）\n  hasSpouse: boolean\n  spouse?: SpouseInfo\n  \n  // 高风险：家庭成员在美情况\n  hasImmediateFamilyInUS: boolean\n  familyInUS?: FamilyMemberInUS[]\n}\n\nexport interface ParentInfo {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  dateOfBirth: string\n  countryOfBirth?: string\n  currentLocation?: string\n  isInUS: boolean\n}\n\nexport interface SpouseInfo {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  dateOfBirth: string\n  nationality: string\n  placeOfBirth: string\n  countryOfBirth: string\n  address: Address\n}\n\nexport interface FamilyMemberInUS {\n  relationship: string\n  name: string\n  status: 'us-citizen' | 'permanent-resident' | 'other'\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 8: 工作/教育\n */\nexport interface Step8Data {\n  currentOccupation: OccupationType\n  \n  // 当前工作/学校\n  employerOrSchool?: EmployerInfo\n  \n  // 高风险：过往雇主（最近5年）\n  hasPreviousEmployment: boolean\n  previousEmployers?: EmployerInfo[]\n  \n  // 教育背景\n  education?: EducationInfo[]\n  \n  // 专业技能\n  hasSpecializedSkills: boolean\n  specializedSkills?: string[]\n}\n\nexport type OccupationType = \n  | 'employed'\n  | 'self-employed'\n  | 'student'\n  | 'retired'\n  | 'unemployed'\n  | 'other'\n\nexport interface EmployerInfo {\n  name: string\n  address: Address\n  phone?: string\n  position: string\n  duties?: string\n  supervisorName?: string\n  supervisorPhone?: string\n  startDate: string\n  endDate?: string\n  monthlySalary?: number\n}\n\nexport interface EducationInfo {\n  institutionName: string\n  address: Address\n  attendanceFrom: string\n  attendanceTo: string\n  degree?: string\n  fieldOfStudy?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 9: 安全问题(1) - 全部高风险\n */\nexport interface Step9Data {\n  // 健康相关\n  hasCommunicableDisease: boolean\n  communicableDiseaseDetails?: string\n  \n  hasMentalDisorder: boolean\n  mentalDisorderDetails?: string\n  \n  isDrugAbuser: boolean\n  drugAbuseDetails?: string\n  \n  // 犯罪记录\n  hasBeenArrested: boolean\n  arrestDetails?: string\n  \n  hasViolatedDrugLaw: boolean\n  drugLawViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 道德问题\n  hasEngagedInProstitution: boolean\n  hasEngagedInHumanTrafficking: boolean\n  hasAssistedInHumanTrafficking: boolean\n  \n  // 洗钱/金融犯罪\n  hasEngagedInMoneyLaundering: boolean\n  moneyLaunderingDetails?: string\n  \n  // 儿童监护\n  hasCommittedChildAbduction: boolean\n  childAbductionDetails?: string\n  \n  // 投票违规\n  hasVotedInViolation: boolean\n  votingViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 公民身份\n  hasRenouncecitizenshipForTax: boolean\n  citizenshipRenunciationDetails?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 10: 安全问题(2) - 全部高风险\n */\nexport interface Step10Data {\n  // 恐怖主义\n  hasEngagedInTerrorism: boolean\n  terrorismDetails?: string\n  \n  hasSupportedTerrorism: boolean\n  terrorismSupportDetails?: string\n  \n  isTerroristOrgMember: boolean\n  terroristOrgDetails?: string\n  \n  // 种族灭绝/酷刑\n  hasCommittedGenocide: boolean\n  genocideDetails?: string\n  \n  hasCommittedTorture: boolean\n  tortureDetails?: string\n  \n  hasCommittedExtrajudicialKilling: boolean\n  killingDetails?: string\n  \n  // 宗教自由\n  hasViolatedReligiousFreedom: boolean\n  religiousFreedomDetails?: string\n  \n  // 强制人口控制\n  hasCoercedTransplantation: boolean\n  transplantationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 签证/移民违规\n  hasBeenDeported: boolean\n  deportationDetails?: string\n  \n  hasViolatedImmigrationLaw: boolean\n  immigrationViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  hasWithheldChildCustody: boolean\n  childCustodyDetails?: string\n  \n  // 签证欺诈\n  hasUsedFraudulentVisa: boolean\n  fraudulentVisaDetails?: string\n  \n  // 非法居留\n  hasOverstayed: boolean\n  overstayDetails?: string\n  \n  // 其他\n  hasBeenDeniedVisa: boolean\n  visaDenialDetails?: string\n  \n  hasBeenDeniedEntry: boolean\n  entryDenialDetails?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 11: 以往旅行\n */\nexport interface Step11Data {\n  // 过去5年访美记录\n  hasVisitedUS: boolean\n  usVisits?: USVisit[]\n  \n  // 过去5年其他国家旅行\n  hasInternationalTravel: boolean\n  internationalTravels?: InternationalTravel[]\n  \n  // 驾照信息\n  hasDriverLicense: boolean\n  driverLicenses?: DriverLicense[]\n}\n\nexport interface USVisit {\n  arrivalDate: string\n  lengthOfStay: number // 天数\n}\n\nexport interface InternationalTravel {\n  country: string\n  arrivalDate: string\n  lengthOfStay: number\n}\n\nexport interface DriverLicense {\n  licenseNumber: string\n  state: string\n  country: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n */\nexport interface Step12Data {\n  // 照片信息\n  photo?: PhotoInfo\n  \n  // 确认声明\n  confirmations: {\n    informationAccurate: boolean\n    understandPenalties: boolean\n    agreeToTerms: boolean\n  }\n  \n  // 签名\n  signature?: string\n  signatureDate?: string\n}\n\nexport interface PhotoInfo {\n  filename: string\n  uploadDate: string\n  size: number\n  mimeType: string\n  dataUrl?: string // Base64编码的图片数据\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 表单校验相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 字段校验规则\n */\nexport interface ValidationRule {\n  required?: boolean\n  pattern?: RegExp\n  minLength?: number\n  maxLength?: number\n  min?: number\n  max?: number\n  custom?: (value: any) => boolean | string\n}\n\n/**\n * 字段校验结果\n */\nexport interface ValidationResult {\n  valid: boolean\n  errors: string[]\n}\n\n/**\n * 步骤校验结果\n */\nexport interface StepValidation {\n  step: number\n  valid: boolean\n  errors: Record<string, string[]>\n  warnings: Record<string, string[]>\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// UI相关类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 步骤信息\n */\nexport interface StepInfo {\n  number: number\n  title: string\n  description: string\n  icon: string\n  completed: boolean\n  hasWarnings: boolean\n}\n\n/**\n * Toast通知类型\n */\nexport type ToastType = 'success' | 'error' | 'warning' | 'info'\n\nexport interface Toast {\n  id: string\n  type: ToastType\n  message: string\n  duration?: number\n}\n\n/**\n * Modal配置\n */\nexport interface ModalConfig {\n  title: string\n  message: string\n  confirmText?: string\n  cancelText?: string\n  type?: 'info' | 'warning' | 'danger'\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 套餐相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 套餐类型\n */\nexport type PlanType = 'free' | 'personal' | 'family'\n\n/**\n * 套餐信息\n */\nexport interface Plan {\n  id: PlanType\n  name: string\n  price: number\n  syncLimit: number | null // null表示无限制\n  features: string[]\n  popular?: boolean\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 同步相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 同步记录\n */\nexport interface SyncRecord {\n  id: string\n  draftId: string\n  timestamp: Date\n  success: boolean\n  errorMessage?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * 同步状态\n */\nexport interface SyncStatus {\n  syncing: boolean\n  lastSyncTime?: Date\n  error?: string\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第二批文件：布局和营销页面\n\n### 7. layouts/default.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\">\n    <!-- 顶部导航 -->\n    <header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\">\n      <nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center h-16\">\n          <!-- Logo -->\n          <NuxtLink to=\"/\" class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n            <Icon name=\"mdi:passport\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600\" />\n            <span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">DS-160 Helper</span>\n          </NuxtLink>\n\n          <!-- 桌面端导航 -->\n          <div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8\">\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/features\"\n              class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors\"\n            >\n              功能介绍\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/pricing\"\n              class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors\"\n            >\n              定价\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n              class=\"btn-primary\"\n            >\n              开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 移动端菜单按钮 -->\n          <button\n            @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = !mobileMenuOpen\"\n            class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100\"\n          >\n            <Icon\n              :name=\"mobileMenuOpen ? 'mdi:close' : 'mdi:menu'\"\n              class=\"w-6 h-6\"\n            />\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 移动端菜单 -->\n        <Transition\n          enter-active-class=\"transition duration-200 ease-out\"\n          enter-from-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n          enter-to-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n          leave-active-class=\"transition duration-100 ease-in\"\n          leave-from-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n          leave-to-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n        >\n          <div v-if=\"mobileMenuOpen\" class=\"md:hidden py-4 space-y-2\">\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/features\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              功能介绍\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/pricing\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              定价\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg text-center\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n        </Transition>\n      </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"flex-1\">\n      <slot />\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-300\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\">\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n          <!-- 公司信息 -->\n          <div class=\"col-span-1 md:col-span-2\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:passport\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-400\" />\n              <span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">DS-160 Helper</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4\">\n              简化DS-160表单填写流程，让签证申请更轻松。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">\n              © 2024 DS-160 Helper. All rights reserved.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 产品 -->\n          <div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">产品</h3>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/features\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  功能介绍\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/pricing\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  定价方案\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/app/dashboard\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  开始使用\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 支持 -->\n          <div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">支持</h3>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">帮助中心</a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">隐私政策</a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">服务条款</a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nconst mobileMenuOpen = ref(false)\n\n// 关闭移动菜单（路由变化时）\nconst route = useRoute()\nwatch(() => route.path, () => {\n  mobileMenuOpen.value = false\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 8. layouts/app.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\">\n    <!-- 顶部导航栏 -->\n    <AppHeader />\n\n    <div class=\"flex\">\n      <!-- 左侧步骤导航 -->\n      <aside\n        class=\"hidden lg:block w-64 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] sticky top-16\"\n      >\n        <StepNavigation />\n      </aside>\n\n      <!-- 主内容区域 -->\n      <main class=\"flex-1 p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n          <slot />\n        </div>\n      </main>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 移动端步骤导航（底部） -->\n    <div class=\"lg:hidden fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white border-t border-gray-200 z-40\">\n      <MobileStepNavigation />\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Toast通知 -->\n    <ToastContainer />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\n// 确保在应用布局中初始化必要的stores\nconst draftStore = useDraftStore()\nconst formStore = useFormStore()\n\n// 页面加载时初始化\nonMounted(() => {\n  draftStore.loadDrafts()\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 9. pages/index.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <!-- Hero Section -->\n    <section class=\"relative bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 text-white overflow-hidden\">\n      <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-grid-white/[0.05] bg-[size:20px_20px]\" />\n      <div class=\"relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28\">\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\n          <h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in\">\n            DS-160 表单填写\n            <br />\n            <span class=\"text-primary-200\">从未如此简单</span>\n          </h1>\n          <p class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up\">\n            智能引导 · 高风险提示 · 自动保存草稿\n            <br />\n            让美国签证申请不再令人头疼\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-slide-up\">\n            <NuxtLink to=\"/app/dashboard\" class=\"btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:rocket-launch\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n              免费开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink to=\"/features\" class=\"btn bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:information\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n              了解更多\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 核心卖点 -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-white\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n            为什么选择 DS-160 Helper？\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n            专为中国申请者设计，解决DS-160表单填写的所有痛点\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:list-box-outline\"\n            title=\"12步智能引导\"\n            description=\"复杂表单拆解为清晰步骤，每步都有中文说明和填写建议\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:alert-circle\"\n            title=\"高风险字段提示\"\n            description=\"自动识别敏感问题，橙色警告框+专业建议，避免拒签风险\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:content-save-outline\"\n            title=\"自动保存草稿\"\n            description=\"实时保存到本地，随时暂停随时