oGen CrewAI LangGraph AG2 开源 multi-agent 框架对比 2026\",\n  \"provider\": \"miaoda\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"CrewAI vs LangGraph vs AutoGen: 2026 Comparison\",\n      \"url\": \"https://agentcenter.cloud/blogs/crewai-vs-langgraph-vs-autogen\",\n      \"description\": \"AG2 is fully open-source with no commercial tier. There's no hosted deployment platform — you manage your own infrastructure.\\nStrengths\\nCompletely free and open-source with no vendor lock-in\\nConversational design is intuitive for multi-agent reasoning and debate\\nExcellent code execution capabilitie...\n- Assistant: 很好，现在我有足够的信息来回答用户了。让我整理一下主流的开源multi-agent框架，并给出对比和推荐。\n\n[[reply_to_current]] \n# 🤖 Agent开发团队开源方案推荐\n\n基于2026年最新情况，给你整理了几个主流的开源multi-agent协作框架：\n\n## 一、主流框架对比\n\n### 1️⃣ **AG2 (AutoGen 2.0)** ⭐️ 推荐首选\n- **GitHub Stars**: 54.7K+\n- **特点**：对话驱动的多Agent协作，\"群聊\"模式\n- **核心优势**：\n  - 微软背书，企业级支持\n  - 原生支持多模型协作（Claude、GPT、Gemini混合编排）\n  - 人机协同开箱即用\n  - 代码执行沙箱，安全可靠\n- **适合场景**：复杂任务拆解、多Agent辩论、动态团队协作\n- **官网**：https://ag2.ai/\n\n### 2️⃣ **CrewAI** \n- **GitHub Stars**: 18K+\n- **特点**：角色驱动，\"像组建团队一样组建Agent\"\n- **核心优势**：\n  - API极简，上手快\n  - 每个Agent定义角色（Role）、目标（Goal）、背景故事（Backstory）\n  - 支持顺序执行（Sequential）和分层执行（Hierarchical）两种模式\n- *...\n\n## Tool Failures\n- cron: Validation failed for tool \"cron\": - action: must be equal to one of the allowed values Received arguments: { \"action\": \"\\n \\n \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t...\n- cron: Validation failed for tool \"cron\": - action: must be equal to one of the allowed values Received arguments: { \"action\": \"\\n \\\"add\\\"\\n \", \"job\": { \"name\": \"每日跨境高溢价工艺品商品推送\", \"schedule\": { \"kind\": \"cron\", \"expr\": \"0 10 * * *\", \"tz\": \"Asia/S...\n- cron: Validation failed for tool \"cron\": - action: must be equal to one of the allowed values Received arguments: { \"action\": \"\\n \\\"list\\\"\\n \", \"includeDisabled\": true }\n\n<read-files>\n~/workspace/agent/extensions/openclaw-extension-miaoda-coding/skills/miaoda-coding/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: System: [2026-04-10 22:59:35 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25 [msg:om_x100b52a54ba68c8cc24719f11c603c5]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52a54ba68c8cc24719f11c603c5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 22:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\"\n}\n```\n\n开始开发 mvp 吧，我...\n- Assistant: 完美！我会用妙搭来开发这个MVP，并且全程让你看到进度和中间结果。根据妙搭的工作方式，我需要先读取相关的skill文档，然后按照正确的流程启动开发。\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): ---\nname: miaoda-coding\ndescription: 用户要求创建或修改应用、网页、页面、PPT、幻灯片、演示文稿，或提到\"妙搭\"、\"vibe coding\"时适用。\nuser-invocable: false\n---\n\n# 妙搭\n\n**重要：创建或修改应用、网页、PPT 等制品的执行环节，必须通过 sessions_spawn 交给妙搭。绝对不要自己动手写代码。**\n\n## 判断是否需要先做前置工作\n\n妙搭只负责**生成制品**（网页、应用、PPT），不负责搜索、分析、总结等研究工作。\n\n收到用户请求后，先判断：\n\n- **纯建站/改站请求**（如\"做一个计算器\"、\"改一下颜色\"）→ 直接派活给妙搭\n- **对话中有需要传递给 code agent 的上下文**（之前讨论的调研结果、用户偏好、素材等）→ 先调 `miaoda_write_reference` 写入参考资料，再派活\n- **复合请求**（如\"先搜集 XX 资料，再生成网站\"）→ 主 agent 先完成研究，**整理为摘要+关键原文引用**，调 `miaoda_write_reference` 写入，再派活\n\n**错误做法**：把\"先搜集再生成\"的整个需求原样丢给妙搭——妙搭不会搜索，只会基于给定内容生成页面。\n\n### 写入参考资料\n\n用 `miaoda_write_reference` 将上下...\n- Assistant: 好的！现在我明白了妙搭的工作流程。让我先把我们之前讨论的DS-160 Helper产品需求整理成参考资料，然后启动开发。\n\n首先，我需要创建一个project_id并整理参考资料：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (miaoda_write_reference): {\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"relativePath\": \"reference/design/001-reference.md\",\n  \"category\": \"design\",\n  \"seq\": 1,\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"totalFiles\": 1,\n    \"categories\": {\n      \"design\": {\n        \"count\": 1,\n        \"files\": [\n          \"001-reference.md\"\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n- Assistant: 很好！现在我再补充一些技术细节和竞品分析：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (miaoda_write_reference): {\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"relativePath\": \"reference/research/001-reference.md\",\n  \"category\": \"research\",\n  \"seq\": 1,\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"totalFiles\": 2,\n    \"categories\": {\n      \"design\": {\n        \"count\": 1,\n        \"files\": [\n          \"001-reference.md\"\n        ]\n      },\n      \"research\": {\n        \"count\": 1,\n        \"files\": [\n          \"001-reference.md\"\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n- Assistant: 完美！参考资料已经准备好了。现在启动妙搭开发MVP：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (sessions_spawn): {\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:5dd1d873-37c6-4044-8cde-7826e18aeb2e\",\n  \"runId\": \"8f723424-7d36-47a9-b854-9e131001d32b\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]]\n✅ **已交给妙搭开发团队！**\n\n## 📋 开发任务\n\n**项目**：DS-160 Helper MVP\n**技术栈**：Nuxt 3 + Vue 3 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS v4\n\n### 核心功能\n- ✓ 12步表单引导填写\n- ✓ 高风险字段智能提示\n- ✓ 草稿自动保存和恢复\n- ✓ 3次模拟同步体验\n- ✓ 响应式设计（移动端友好）\n\n### 页面结构\n**营销页（SSR）**：首页、功能介绍、定价页\n**应用页（CSR）**：表单填写、草稿管理\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 进度可见性\n\n妙搭会：\n1. **实时推送进度**到你的飞书（每个关键步骤完成会通知）\n2. **中间结果可见**：每完成一个模块会有预览链接\n3. **最终交付**：完整的可运行应用 + 代码\n\n你会收到类似这样的进度通知：\n- \"✓ 项目初始化完成\"\n- \"✓ 营销页面完成（首页、功能介绍、定价）\"\n- \"✓ 表单第1-4步完成\"\n- \"✓ 表单第5-8步完成\"\n- ...\n\n**预计时间**：15-30分钟（取决于项目复杂度）\n\n现在请等待妙搭的进度推送，我会在这里陪着你，有任何问题随时问我！\n\n🦞\n\n<read-files>\n~/workspace/agent/extensions/openclaw-extension-miaoda-coding/skills/miaoda-coding/SKILL.md\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"274e09b6","tokensBefore":168197,"details":{"readFiles":["~/workspace/agent/extensions/openclaw-extension-miaoda-coding/skills/miaoda-coding/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
