{"type":"message","id":"79cfcdcd","parentId":"242da8d7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:54:01.465Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_016CT47GDE3eaabGrcANPKp8","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"8a38a77e-1576-4380-899a-9a0b3dd91c95\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\",\n  \"name\": \"AG2开发任务监控\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1775840041454,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1775840041454,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"*/5 * * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"检查AG2开发任务状态：1) 检查young-river进程是否还在运行 2) 读取ag2-output.log最后50行 3) 检查outputs/ds160-helper/目录内容 4) 如果任务完成或出错，立即向用户汇报详细结果和下一步建议\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"to\": \"user:ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775840100000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"8a38a77e-1576-4380-899a-9a0b3dd91c95","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25","name":"AG2开发任务监控","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1775840041454,"updatedAtMs":1775840041454,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"*/5 * * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"检查AG2开发任务状态：1) 检查young-river进程是否还在运行 2) 读取ag2-output.log最后50行 3) 检查outputs/ds160-helper/目录内容 4) 如果任务完成或出错，立即向用户汇报详细结果和下一步建议","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"user:ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1775840100000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775840041459}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b7c6c80","parentId":"79cfcdcd","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:54:24.122Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 方案3：修复AG2配置，重新运行🔧\n\n现在最重要的是：**AG2失败了，我们需要修复它**。问题是`human_input_mode`设置错误。\n\n让我现在就给你完整的答复：\n\n[[reply_to_current]]\n# ⏰ 00:52 - 关于定时跟进 & AG2任务失败分析\n\n## 你的问题：怎么才能真的定时跟进？\n\n我刚才确实没有主动跟进，原因是：\n1. ❌ 我的`HEARTBEAT.md`是空的，没有检查清单\n2. ❌ 没有设置针对性的cron任务\n3. ❌ AG2在后台静默失败，我没有察觉\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 现在已修复\n\n### 1. 已更新 HEARTBEAT.md\n每次心跳（约30分钟）会自动检查：\n- 后台任务进度\n- AG2日志更新\n- 项目目录变化\n\n### 2. 已创建Cron任务\n**\"AG2开发任务监控\"** - 每5分钟检查一次\n- 下次运行：00:55\n- 会自动检查进程、日志、输出目录\n- 发现完成或出错会立即通知你\n\n---\n\n## ❌ AG2任务失败原因\n\n刚才检查了日志，发现**AG2在00:10就失败了**：\n\n```\nEOFError: EOF when reading a line\n```\n\n**问题**：`UserProxyAgent`的`human_input_mode=\"TERMINATE\"`配置错误\n- 它试图等待人类输入\n- 但在后台运行时没有stdin，导致EOF错误\n- Frontend Developer生成了大量代码（日志里能看到），但最后崩溃了\n\n**结果**：`outputs/ds160-helper/`目录是空的，代码没有真正写入文件\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 修复方案\n\n我需要修改`main.py`中的UserProxyAgent配置：\n\n**错误配置**：\n```python\nhuman_input_mode=\"TERMINATE\"  # 会等待输入\n```\n\n**正确配置**：\n```python\nhuman_input_mode=\"NEVER\"  # 永不等待输入，全自动\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💡 现在怎么办？\n\n### 选项A：修复AG2重新运行（推荐）\n1. 我修改`main.py`配置\n2. 重新运行AG2团队\n3. 这次会完全自动化，不会卡住\n\n### 选项B：手动提取已生成的代码\nFrontend Developer实际上已经在日志里生成了很多代码，我可以：\n1. 从日志中提取代码\n2. 手动创建文件\n3. 推送到GitHub\n\n**选项A更干净，选项B更快。你想要哪个？**\n\n---\n\n## 📊 监控现状\n\n✅ **HEARTBEAT已配置**（30分钟轮询）\n✅ **Cron已设置**（5分钟轮询AG2任务）\n✅ **下次自动检查**：00:55\n\n从现在开始，我会主动跟进长时间任务的进度。\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"erda","model":"anthropic/us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0","usage":{"input":116342,"output":928,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117270,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775840041464}}
