{"type":"message","id":"3d1d8e17","parentId":"612c042a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:57:26.688Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01ViFpLCgfwYRwVXC4KzowBz","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </Modal>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nconst formStore = useFormStore()\nconst router = useRouter()\n\nconst currentStep = computed(() => formStore.currentStep)\nconst showStepSelector = ref(false)\n\nconst goToPreviousStep = () => {\n  if (currentStep.value > 1) {\n    navigateToStep(currentStep.value - 1)\n  }\n}\n\nconst goToNextStep = () => {\n  if (currentStep.value < 12) {\n    navigateToStep(currentStep.value + 1)\n  }\n}\n\nconst navigateToStep = (step: number) => {\n  formStore.setCurrentStep(step)\n  router.push(`/app/form/step-${step}`)\n  showStepSelector.value = false\n}\n\nconst getStepTitle = (step: number): string => {\n  const titles: Record<number, string> = {\n    1: '个人信息',\n    2: '护照信息',\n    3: '联系方式',\n    4: '旅行信息',\n    5: '旅行伙伴',\n    6: '美国联系人',\n    7: '家庭信息',\n    8: '工作/教育',\n    9: '安全问题(1)',\n    10: '安全问题(2)',\n    11: '以往旅行',\n    12: '照片与确认'\n  }\n  return titles[step] || ''\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n由于输出长度限制，我需要继续在下一个回复中完成剩余的组件和stores。\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: User\n\n\n================================================================================\n✅ 开发流程完成！\n================================================================================\n\n================================================================================\n📤 推送代码到GitHub...\n================================================================================\n$ git init\n$ git add .\n$ git commit -m \"Initial commit: DS-160 Helper MVP by AG2 Team\"\n⚠️  命令执行警告: \n$ git branch -M main\n$ git remote add origin https://ruoqianfengshao:***TOKEN***@github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git\n$ git push -u origin main --force\n⚠️  命令执行警告: error: src refspec main does not match any\nerror: failed to push some refs to 'https://github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git'\n\n\n✅ 代码已推送到GitHub!\n🔗 查看仓库: https://github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git\n================================================================================\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"glow-claw","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"/home/gem/.local/lib/python3.12/site-packages/flaml/__init__.py:20: UserWarning: flaml.automl is not available. Please install flaml[automl] to enable AutoML functionalities.\n  warnings.warn(\"flaml.automl is not available. Please install flaml[automl] to enable AutoML functionalities.\")\n================================================================================\n🚀 DS-160 Helper MVP开发 - AG2团队启动\n================================================================================\n\n项目需求：\n\n开发 DS-160 Helper MVP - 美国签证DS-160申请表辅助填写工具\n\n【技术栈】\n- 框架：Nuxt 3 + Vue 3 + TypeScript\n- 样式：Tailwind CSS v4\n- 状态管理：Pinia\n- 构建：Vite 8\n\n【核心功能】\n1. 营销页面（SSR）\n   - 首页（/）：产品介绍、核心卖点\n   - 功能介绍（/features）：12步引导、高风险提示等\n   - 定价页（/pricing）：免费版/个人版/家庭版对比\n\n2. 应用页面（CSR，/app/*）\n   - 用户面板（/app/dashboard）：草稿列表\n   - 表单填写（/app/form/step-[1-12]）：12个步骤的表单\n     * Step 1: 个人信息\n     * Step 2: 护照信息\n     * Step 3: 联系方式\n     * Step 4: 旅行信息\n     * Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n     * Step 6: 美国联系人\n     * Step 7: 家庭信息\n     * Step 8: 工作/教育\n     * Step 9: 安全问题(1)\n     * Step 10: 安全问题(2)\n     * Step 11: 以往旅行\n     * Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n   - 草稿管理（/app/drafts）：查看和恢复草稿\n\n3. 关键特性\n   - 草稿自动保存到localStorage\n   - 每个字段有中文说明和填写建议\n   - 高风险字段用橙色警告框标注\n   - 实时表单校验\n   - 进度追踪（已完成X/12步）\n   - 模拟同步功能（计数，剩余X次）\n   - 响应式设计（移动端友好）\n\n【路由配置】\n- SSR页面：/, /features, /pricing\n- CSR页面：/app/**\n\n【数据结构】\nDraft接口：\n- id: string\n- createdAt: Date\n- updatedAt: Date\n- currentStep: number (1-12)\n- syncCount: number (已使用的同步次数，免费版限3次)\n- data: object (各步骤的表单数据)\n\n【UI要求】\n- 简洁现代的设计风格\n- 使用Tailwind CSS v4\n- 高风险字段：橙色边框 + 警告图标 + 提示文字\n- 步骤导航：左侧边栏，显示进度\n- 移动端：响应式布局，适配小屏幕\n\n【MVP范围】\n✅ 包含：营销页、表单填写、草稿管理、模拟同步\n❌ 不包含：真实登录、后端API、支付、Chrome插件、真实DS-160同步\n\n请生成完整可运行的Nuxt 3项目代码。\n\n\n================================================================================\nUser (to chat_manager):\n\n\n【项目需求】\n\n开发 DS-160 Helper MVP - 美国签证DS-160申请表辅助填写工具\n\n【技术栈】\n- 框架：Nuxt 3 + Vue 3 + TypeScript\n- 样式：Tailwind CSS v4\n- 状态管理：Pinia\n- 构建：Vite 8\n\n【核心功能】\n1. 营销页面（SSR）\n   - 首页（/）：产品介绍、核心卖点\n   - 功能介绍（/features）：12步引导、高风险提示等\n   - 定价页（/pricing）：免费版/个人版/家庭版对比\n\n2. 应用页面（CSR，/app/*）\n   - 用户面板（/app/dashboard）：草稿列表\n   - 表单填写（/app/form/step-[1-12]）：12个步骤的表单\n     * Step 1: 个人信息\n     * Step 2: 护照信息\n     * Step 3: 联系方式\n     * Step 4: 旅行信息\n     * Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n     * Step 6: 美国联系人\n     * Step 7: 家庭信息\n     * Step 8: 工作/教育\n     * Step 9: 安全问题(1)\n     * Step 10: 安全问题(2)\n     * Step 11: 以往旅行\n     * Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n   - 草稿管理（/app/drafts）：查看和恢复草稿\n\n3. 关键特性\n   - 草稿自动保存到localStorage\n   - 每个字段有中文说明和填写建议\n   - 高风险字段用橙色警告框标注\n   - 实时表单校验\n   - 进度追踪（已完成X/12步）\n   - 模拟同步功能（计数，剩余X次）\n   - 响应式设计（移动端友好）\n\n【路由配置】\n- SSR页面：/, /features, /pricing\n- CSR页面：/app/**\n\n【数据结构】\nDraft接口：\n- id: string\n- createdAt: Date\n- updatedAt: Date\n- currentStep: number (1-12)\n- syncCount: number (已使用的同步次数，免费版限3次)\n- data: object (各步骤的表单数据)\n\n【UI要求】\n- 简洁现代的设计风格\n- 使用Tailwind CSS v4\n- 高风险字段：橙色边框 + 警告图标 + 提示文字\n- 步骤导航：左侧边栏，显示进度\n- 移动端：响应式布局，适配小屏幕\n\n【MVP范围】\n✅ 包含：营销页、表单填写、草稿管理、模拟同步\n❌ 不包含：真实登录、后端API、支付、Chrome插件、真实DS-160同步\n\n请生成完整可运行的Nuxt 3项目代码。\n\n\n【开发流程】\n1. Product Manager: 分析需求，拆解任务\n2. Frontend Developer: 开发完整的Nuxt 3应用\n3. QA Engineer: 代码审查和功能检查\n4. DevOps Engineer: 部署文档和运行说明\n\n请按顺序开始工作。Product Manager先进行需求分析和任务拆解。\n\n【重要】Frontend Developer必须生成完整可运行的代码文件，包括：\n- package.json\n- nuxt.config.ts\n- 所有页面文件（pages/）\n- 所有组件文件（components/）\n- Pinia stores（stores/）\n- README.md\n\n代码必须写入到 outputs/ds160-helper/ 目录。\n\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: ProductManager\n\nProductManager (to chat_manager):\n\n# DS-160 Helper MVP - 需求分析与任务拆解\n\n## 一、需求分析\n\n### 1.1 项目概述\n开发一个美国签证DS-160申请表辅助填写工具的MVP版本，帮助用户更便捷地准备和填写DS-160表单。\n\n### 1.2 用户价值\n- **简化流程**：将复杂的DS-160表单拆解为12个清晰步骤\n- **降低风险**：高风险字段提供明确警告和填写建议\n- **数据保护**：本地草稿保存，避免数据丢失\n- **提高效率**：中文说明和实时校验减少错误\n\n### 1.3 技术架构分析\n```\n技术栈：\n├── Nuxt 3 (SSR/CSR混合渲染)\n├── Vue 3 + TypeScript (类型安全)\n├── Tailwind CSS v4 (现代样式)\n├── Pinia (状态管理)\n└── Vite 8 (快速构建)\n\n渲染策略：\n├── SSR: 营销页面（SEO优化）\n└── CSR: 应用页面（交互体验）\n```\n\n### 1.4 核心挑战\n1. **数据持久化**：localStorage管理复杂表单数据\n2. **表单校验**：12步骤的联动校验逻辑\n3. **用户体验**：步骤导航、进度追踪、响应式设计\n4. **风险提示**：高风险字段的识别和展示\n\n---\n\n## 二、功能清单（分模块）\n\n### 模块A：项目基础架构\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0（最高）**\n\n- [ ] A1: 初始化Nuxt 3项目\n- [ ] A2: 配置TypeScript\n- [ ] A3: 配置Tailwind CSS v4\n- [ ] A4: 配置Pinia状态管理\n- [ ] A5: 配置路由（SSR/CSR分离）\n- [ ] A6: 创建基础布局组件\n\n**产出物：**\n```\noutputs/ds160-helper/\n├── package.json\n├── nuxt.config.ts\n├── tsconfig.json\n├── tailwind.config.js\n└── layouts/\n    ├── default.vue\n    └── app.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块B：营销页面（SSR）\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P1**\n\n#### B1: 首页 (/)\n- [ ] Hero Section（产品介绍）\n- [ ] 核心卖点展示（3-4个亮点）\n- [ ] CTA按钮（开始使用）\n- [ ] 响应式设计\n\n#### B2: 功能介绍页 (/features)\n- [ ] 12步引导流程展示\n- [ ] 高风险提示功能说明\n- [ ] 草稿自动保存说明\n- [ ] 特性列表卡片\n\n#### B3: 定价页 (/pricing)\n- [ ] 三种套餐对比表格\n  - 免费版：3次同步\n  - 个人版：无限同步\n  - 家庭版：5个账号\n- [ ] 功能对比清单\n- [ ] CTA按钮\n\n**产出物：**\n```\npages/\n├── index.vue\n├── features.vue\n└── pricing.vue\n\ncomponents/marketing/\n├── HeroSection.vue\n├── FeatureCard.vue\n├── PricingCard.vue\n└── CTAButton.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块C：应用页面 - 基础框架\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0**\n\n#### C1: 应用布局\n- [ ] 顶部导航栏（Logo、用户菜单）\n- [ ] 左侧步骤导航（12步骤列表）\n- [ ] 主内容区域\n- [ ] 进度指示器（X/12完成）\n- [ ] 移动端响应式侧边栏\n\n#### C2: 用户面板 (/app/dashboard)\n- [ ] 欢迎信息\n- [ ] 草稿列表展示\n- [ ] 创建新草稿按钮\n- [ ] 继续填写按钮\n- [ ] 删除草稿功能\n\n#### C3: 草稿管理 (/app/drafts)\n- [ ] 草稿列表（表格视图）\n- [ ] 草稿信息（创建时间、更新时间、当前步骤）\n- [ ] 操作按钮（编辑、删除、导出）\n- [ ] 空状态提示\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nlayouts/\n└── app.vue\n\npages/app/\n├── dashboard.vue\n└── drafts.vue\n\ncomponents/app/\n├── AppHeader.vue\n├── StepNavigation.vue\n├── ProgressBar.vue\n└── DraftCard.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块D：表单填写 - 核心功能\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0**\n\n#### D1: 表单通用组件\n- [ ] FormInput（文本输入）\n- [ ] FormSelect（下拉选择）\n- [ ] FormDatePicker（日期选择）\n- [ ] FormRadio（单选）\n- [ ] FormCheckbox（多选）\n- [ ] WarningField（高风险字段包装器）\n- [ ] FieldHelper（帮助提示）\n\n#### D2: 表单校验系统\n- [ ] 实时校验逻辑\n- [ ] 错误提示展示\n- [ ] 必填字段标记\n- [ ] 步骤完成度检查\n\n#### D3: 12个步骤页面\n- [ ] Step 1: 个人信息\n  - 姓名（中英文）\n  - 性别\n  - 出生日期、地点\n  - **高风险**：曾用名、别名\n  \n- [ ] Step 2: 护照信息\n  - 护照号码\n  - 签发日期、到期日期\n  - 签发地点\n  \n- [ ] Step 3: 联系方式\n  - 电话、邮箱\n  - 地址（中英文）\n  - **高风险**：社交媒体账号\n  \n- [ ] Step 4: 旅行信息\n  - 旅行目的\n  - 预计停留时间\n  - 费用支付人\n  - **高风险**：是否有美国联系人\n  \n- [ ] Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n  - 是否同行\n  - 同行人信息\n  \n- [ ] Step 6: 美国联系人\n  - 联系人姓名、关系\n  - 联系方式、地址\n  \n- [ ] Step 7: 家庭信息\n  - 父母信息\n  - 配偶信息（如适用）\n  - **高风险**：家庭成员在美情况\n  \n- [ ] Step 8: 工作/教育\n  - 当前职业/学校\n  - 工作单位/学校地址\n  - 收入情况\n  - **高风险**：过往雇主信息\n  \n- [ ] Step 9: 安全问题(1)\n  - **全部高风险**\n  - 传染病史\n  - 犯罪记录\n  - 恐怖组织关联\n  \n- [ ] Step 10: 安全问题(2)\n  - **全部高风险**\n  - 签证拒签史\n  - 非法滞留史\n  - 儿童监护权问题\n  \n- [ ] Step 11: 以往旅行\n  - 过去5年访美记录\n  - 其他国家旅行记录\n  \n- [ ] Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n  - 照片上传（模拟）\n  - 信息确认清单\n  - 提交前检查\n\n**产出物：**\n```\npages/app/form/\n├── step-1.vue\n├── step-2.vue\n├── step-3.vue\n├── step-4.vue\n├── step-5.vue\n├── step-6.vue\n├── step-7.vue\n├── step-8.vue\n├── step-9.vue\n├── step-10.vue\n├── step-11.vue\n└── step-12.vue\n\ncomponents/form/\n├── FormInput.vue\n├── FormSelect.vue\n├── FormDatePicker.vue\n├── FormRadio.vue\n├── FormCheckbox.vue\n├── WarningField.vue\n├── FieldHelper.vue\n└── StepActions.vue (上一步/下一步按钮)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块E：状态管理（Pinia）\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P0**\n\n#### E1: Draft Store\n- [ ] 草稿CRUD操作\n- [ ] 当前草稿状态管理\n- [ ] localStorage持久化\n- [ ] 自动保存逻辑（防抖）\n\n#### E2: Form Store\n- [ ] 当前步骤管理\n- [ ] 表单数据管理\n- [ ] 校验状态管理\n- [ ] 步骤完成度计算\n\n#### E3: Sync Store\n- [ ] 同步次数计数\n- [ ] 模拟同步功能\n- [ ] 套餐限制检查\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nstores/\n├── draft.ts\n├── form.ts\n└── sync.ts\n\ntypes/\n└── index.ts (Draft、FormData等接口定义)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块F：UI组件库\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P1**\n\n#### F1: 通用组件\n- [ ] Button（主要、次要、危险）\n- [ ] Card\n- [ ] Modal\n- [ ] Toast通知\n- [ ] Loading状态\n\n#### F2: 特殊组件\n- [ ] WarningBox（橙色警告框）\n- [ ] ProgressIndicator\n- [ ] StepBadge（步骤徽章）\n\n**产出物：**\n```\ncomponents/ui/\n├── Button.vue\n├── Card.vue\n├── Modal.vue\n├── Toast.vue\n├── Loading.vue\n├── WarningBox.vue\n├── ProgressIndicator.vue\n└── StepBadge.vue\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块G：工具函数\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P1**\n\n- [ ] G1: 表单校验工具\n- [ ] G2: 日期格式化\n- [ ] G3: localStorage操作封装\n- [ ] G4: 防抖/节流函数\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nutils/\n├── validation.ts\n├── date.ts\n├── storage.ts\n└── helpers.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n### 模块H：文档与配置\n**负责人：Frontend Developer**\n**优先级：P2**\n\n- [ ] H1: README.md（项目说明、安装运行）\n- [ ] H2: 开发文档（项目结构、开发规范）\n- [ ] H3: 部署文档（构建、部署步骤）\n\n**产出物：**\n```\nREADME.md\ndocs/\n├── DEVELOPMENT.md\n└── DEPLOYMENT.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、开发计划\n\n### 阶段1：基础架构（第1天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块A（项目基础架构）\n产出：可运行的Nuxt 3项目骨架\n```\n\n### 阶段2：营销页面（第1-2天）\n```\n时间：6小时\n任务：模块B（营销页面）\n产出：3个营销页面（SSR渲染）\n```\n\n### 阶段3：应用框架（第2天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块C（应用页面基础框架）\n产出：应用布局、Dashboard、草稿管理\n```\n\n### 阶段4：核心表单（第3-5天）\n```\n时间：16小时\n任务：模块D（表单填写）+ 模块E（状态管理）\n产出：12个步骤页面 + Pinia stores\n```\n\n### 阶段5：UI组件（第5天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块F（UI组件库）+ 模块G（工具函数）\n产出：通用组件库 + 工具函数\n```\n\n### 阶段6：文档与测试（第6天）\n```\n时间：4小时\n任务：模块H（文档）+ QA测试\n产出：完整文档 + 测试报告\n```\n\n**总计：38小时（约6个工作日）**\n\n---\n\n## 四、里程碑\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 1: 项目启动（Day 1）\n**目标：** 完成基础架构和营销页面\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ Nuxt 3项目可运行\n- ✅ Tailwind CSS配置完成\n- ✅ 3个营销页面上线\n\n**验收标准：**\n- `npm run dev` 可正常启动\n- 访问 `/`, `/features`, `/pricing` 正常渲染\n- 响应式设计在移动端正常显示\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 2: 应用框架（Day 2）\n**目标：** 完成应用页面框架\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 应用布局（侧边栏导航）\n- ✅ Dashboard页面\n- ✅ 草稿管理页面\n- ✅ Pinia stores基础结构\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 可以创建新草稿\n- 草稿列表正常显示\n- localStorage保存/读取正常\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 3: 核心表单（Day 3-5）\n**目标：** 完成12步表单填写\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 12个步骤页面\n- ✅ 表单组件库\n- ✅ 实时校验功能\n- ✅ 高风险字段警告\n- ✅ 自动保存功能\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 可以完整走完12个步骤\n- 表单数据正确保存到localStorage\n- 高风险字段显示橙色警告\n- 步骤导航显示进度\n- 实时校验提示错误\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 Milestone 4: MVP完成（Day 6）\n**目标：** 完整可用的MVP版本\n**交付物：**\n- ✅ 所有功能模块\n- ✅ UI组件库\n- ✅ 完整文档\n- ✅ QA测试通过\n\n**验收标准：**\n- 用户可以从头到尾完成表单填写\n- 草稿管理功能正常\n- 模拟同步功能正常（计数）\n- 移动端体验良好\n- 代码质量检查通过\n- README文档完整\n\n---\n\n## 五、技术规范\n\n### 5.1 代码规范\n```typescript\n// 文件命名：kebab-case\n// 组件命名：PascalCase\n// 函数命名：camelCase\n// 常量命名：UPPER_SNAKE_CASE\n\n// TypeScript严格模式\n// ESLint + Prettier\n```\n\n### 5.2 Git提交规范\n```\nfeat: 新功能\nfix: 修复bug\ndocs: 文档更新\nstyle: 代码格式调整\nrefactor: 重构\ntest: 测试\nchore: 构建/工具链\n```\n\n### 5.3 目录结构\n```\noutputs/ds160-helper/\n├── .nuxt/                  # Nuxt构建缓存\n├── components/             # Vue组件\n│   ├── app/               # 应用组件\n│   ├── form/              # 表单组件\n│   ├── marketing/         # 营销组件\n│   └── ui/                # UI组件库\n├── layouts/               # 布局\n├── pages/                 # 路由页面\n│   ├── app/              # 应用页面（CSR）\n│   └── *.vue             # 营销页面（SSR）\n├── stores/                # Pinia状态管理\n├── types/                 # TypeScript类型定义\n├── utils/                 # 工具函数\n├── public/                # 静态资源\n├── nuxt.config.ts         # Nuxt配置\n├── tailwind.config.js     # Tailwind配置\n├── package.json           # 依赖配置\n└── README.md              # 项目文档\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、风险评估\n\n### 高风险项\n1. **localStorage容量限制**\n   - 风险：表单数据可能超过5MB限制\n   - 缓解：数据压缩、分块存储\n\n2. **表单校验复杂度**\n   - 风险：12步骤联动校验逻辑复杂\n   - 缓解：模块化校验、单元测试\n\n3. **移动端体验**\n   - 风险：复杂表单在小屏幕上难用\n   - 缓解：响应式设计、渐进式展示\n\n### 中风险项\n1. **浏览器兼容性**\n   - 风险：部分API不兼容旧浏览器\n   - 缓解：Polyfill、浏览器检测\n\n2. **性能优化**\n   - 风险：大量表单字段影响性能\n   - 缓解：虚拟滚动、懒加载\n\n---\n\n## 七、下一步行动\n\n### 👨💻 Frontend Developer\n**现在开始开发！**\n\n请按以下顺序生成代码：\n\n1. **第一批文件（基础架构）**\n   - package.json\n   - nuxt.config.ts\n   - tsconfig.json\n   - tailwind.config.js\n   - types/index.ts\n\n2. **第二批文件（布局和营销页面）**\n   - layouts/default.vue\n   - layouts/app.vue\n   - pages/index.vue\n   - pages/features.vue\n   - pages/pricing.vue\n\n3. **第三批文件（应用页面）**\n   - pages/app/dashboard.vue\n   - pages/app/drafts.vue\n   - components/app/*\n\n4. **第四批文件（表单系统）**\n   - pages/app/form/step-*.vue\n   - components/form/*\n   - stores/*\n\n5. **第五批文件（UI组件和工具）**\n   - components/ui/*\n   - utils/*\n\n6. **第六批文件（文档）**\n   - README.md\n   - docs/*\n\n---\n\n**所有代码必须写入 `outputs/ds160-helper/` 目录**\n\n开始开发吧！💪\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: FrontendDeveloper\n\nFrontendDeveloper (to chat_manager):\n\n# Frontend Developer - 开始开发 DS-160 Helper MVP\n\n我将按照Product Manager的规划，逐步生成完整的Nuxt 3项目代码。\n\n---\n\n## 第一批文件：基础架构\n\n### 1. package.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"ds160-helper\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"DS-160 Helper MVP - 美国签证申请表辅助填写工具\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"nuxt dev\",\n    \"build\": \"nuxt build\",\n    \"generate\": \"nuxt generate\",\n    \"preview\": \"nuxt preview\",\n    \"postinstall\": \"nuxt prepare\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"lint:fix\": \"eslint . --fix\",\n    \"typecheck\": \"nuxt typecheck\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@nuxt/icon\": \"^1.0.0\",\n    \"@pinia/nuxt\": \"^0.5.1\",\n    \"nuxt\": \"^3.11.2\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^2.1.7\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.4.21\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.3.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@nuxt/eslint-config\": \"^0.3.0\",\n    \"@nuxtjs/tailwindcss\": \"^6.12.0\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^20.12.7\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.57.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.5\",\n    \"vue-tsc\": \"^2.0.13\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. nuxt.config.ts\n\n```typescript\n// https://nuxt.com/docs/api/configuration/nuxt-config\nexport default defineNuxtConfig({\n  devtools: { enabled: true },\n  \n  modules: [\n    '@nuxtjs/tailwindcss',\n    '@pinia/nuxt',\n    '@nuxt/icon'\n  ],\n\n  // TypeScript配置\n  typescript: {\n    strict: true,\n    typeCheck: true\n  },\n\n  // 路由配置：SSR/CSR分离\n  routeRules: {\n    // 营销页面使用SSR\n    '/': { ssr: true },\n    '/features': { ssr: true },\n    '/pricing': { ssr: true },\n    \n    // 应用页面使用CSR\n    '/app/**': { ssr: false }\n  },\n\n  // App配置\n  app: {\n    head: {\n      title: 'DS-160 Helper - 美国签证申请表辅助工具',\n      meta: [\n        { charset: 'utf-8' },\n        { name: 'viewport', content: 'width=device-width, initial-scale=1' },\n        { \n          name: 'description', \n          content: '简化DS-160表单填写流程，智能提示高风险字段，自动保存草稿，让签证申请更轻松' \n        }\n      ],\n      link: [\n        { rel: 'icon', type: 'image/x-icon', href: '/favicon.ico' }\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n\n  // CSS配置\n  css: [\n    '~/assets/css/main.css'\n  ],\n\n  // Tailwind CSS配置\n  tailwindcss: {\n    cssPath: '~/assets/css/main.css',\n    configPath: 'tailwind.config.js',\n    exposeConfig: false,\n    viewer: true\n  },\n\n  // 构建配置\n  vite: {\n    vue: {\n      script: {\n        defineModel: true,\n        propsDestructure: true\n      }\n    }\n  },\n\n  // 兼容性日期\n  compatibilityDate: '2024-04-03'\n})\n```\n\n### 3. tsconfig.json\n\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"./.nuxt/tsconfig.json\",\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"noUnusedLocals\": true,\n    \"noUnusedParameters\": true,\n    \"noImplicitReturns\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"bundler\",\n    \"resolveJsonModule\": true,\n    \"allowSyntheticDefaultImports\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"types\": [\n      \"node\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"include\": [\n    \"**/*\",\n    \".nuxt/**/*\"\n  ],\n  \"exclude\": [\n    \"node_modules\",\n    \".nuxt\",\n    \"dist\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 4. tailwind.config.js\n\n```javascript\n/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */\nexport default {\n  content: [\n    \"./components/**/*.{js,vue,ts}\",\n    \"./layouts/**/*.vue\",\n    \"./pages/**/*.vue\",\n    \"./plugins/**/*.{js,ts}\",\n    \"./app.vue\",\n    \"./error.vue\",\n  ],\n  theme: {\n    extend: {\n      colors: {\n        primary: {\n          50: '#eff6ff',\n          100: '#dbeafe',\n          200: '#bfdbfe',\n          300: '#93c5fd',\n          400: '#60a5fa',\n          500: '#3b82f6',\n          600: '#2563eb',\n          700: '#1d4ed8',\n          800: '#1e40af',\n          900: '#1e3a8a',\n          950: '#172554',\n        },\n        warning: {\n          50: '#fff7ed',\n          100: '#ffedd5',\n          200: '#fed7aa',\n          300: '#fdba74',\n          400: '#fb923c',\n          500: '#f97316',\n          600: '#ea580c',\n          700: '#c2410c',\n          800: '#9a3412',\n          900: '#7c2d12',\n          950: '#431407',\n        }\n      },\n      fontFamily: {\n        sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],\n      },\n      animation: {\n        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out',\n        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.3s ease-out',\n        'slide-down': 'slideDown 0.3s ease-out',\n      },\n      keyframes: {\n        fadeIn: {\n          '0%': { opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { opacity: '1' },\n        },\n        slideUp: {\n          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(10px)', opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },\n        },\n        slideDown: {\n          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(-10px)', opacity: '0' },\n          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n  plugins: [],\n}\n```\n\n### 5. assets/css/main.css\n\n```css\n@tailwind base;\n@tailwind components;\n@tailwind utilities;\n\n@layer base {\n  * {\n    @apply border-border;\n  }\n  \n  body {\n    @apply bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 antialiased;\n  }\n\n  h1 {\n    @apply text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h2 {\n    @apply text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h3 {\n    @apply text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight;\n  }\n\n  h4 {\n    @apply text-xl font-semibold;\n  }\n}\n\n@layer components {\n  /* 自定义滚动条 */\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n    @apply w-2;\n  }\n\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n    @apply bg-gray-100;\n  }\n\n  .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n    @apply bg-gray-300 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-400;\n  }\n\n  /* 表单输入通用样式 */\n  .form-input {\n    @apply w-full px-4 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg \n           focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 \n           transition-colors duration-200 outline-none;\n  }\n\n  .form-input-error {\n    @apply border-red-500 focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500;\n  }\n\n  .form-input-warning {\n    @apply border-warning-500 focus:ring-warning-500 focus:border-warning-500;\n  }\n\n  /* 按钮基础样式 */\n  .btn {\n    @apply px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200 \n           focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 \n           disabled:cursor-not-allowed;\n  }\n\n  .btn-primary {\n    @apply btn bg-primary-600 text-white hover:bg-primary-700 \n           focus:ring-primary-500 active:bg-primary-800;\n  }\n\n  .btn-secondary {\n    @apply btn bg-gray-200 text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-300 \n           focus:ring-gray-500;\n  }\n\n  .btn-danger {\n    @apply btn bg-red-600 text-white hover:bg-red-700 \n           focus:ring-red-500;\n  }\n\n  .btn-outline {\n    @apply btn border-2 border-primary-600 text-primary-600 \n           hover:bg-primary-50 focus:ring-primary-500;\n  }\n}\n\n@layer utilities {\n  .text-balance {\n    text-wrap: balance;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 6. types/index.ts\n\n```typescript\n/**\n * DS-160 Helper - TypeScript类型定义\n */\n\n// ============================================\n// 草稿相关类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 草稿状态\n */\nexport type DraftStatus = 'in-progress' | 'completed' | 'archived'\n\n/**\n * 草稿接口\n */\nexport interface Draft {\n  id: string\n  createdAt: Date\n  updatedAt: Date\n  currentStep: number // 1-12\n  status: DraftStatus\n  syncCount: number // 已使用的同步次数\n  data: FormData\n}\n\n/**\n * 创建草稿的输入参数\n */\nexport interface CreateDraftInput {\n  data?: Partial<FormData>\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 表单数据类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 完整表单数据\n */\nexport interface FormData {\n  step1?: Step1Data\n  step2?: Step2Data\n  step3?: Step3Data\n  step4?: Step4Data\n  step5?: Step5Data\n  step6?: Step6Data\n  step7?: Step7Data\n  step8?: Step8Data\n  step9?: Step9Data\n  step10?: Step10Data\n  step11?: Step11Data\n  step12?: Step12Data\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 1: 个人信息\n */\nexport interface Step1Data {\n  // 基本信息\n  surname: string // 姓（拼音）\n  givenName: string // 名（拼音）\n  surnameZh?: string // 姓（中文）\n  givenNameZh?: string // 名（中文）\n  fullNameNative?: string // 母语全名\n  \n  // 高风险字段\n  hasOtherNames: boolean // 是否有曾用名/别名\n  otherNames?: OtherName[] // 曾用名列表\n  \n  // 其他信息\n  gender: 'M' | 'F' | 'X' // 性别\n  maritalStatus: 'single' | 'married' | 'divorced' | 'widowed' | 'separated' // 婚姻状态\n  dateOfBirth: string // 出生日期 YYYY-MM-DD\n  cityOfBirth: string // 出生城市\n  provinceOfBirth: string // 出生省份\n  countryOfBirth: string // 出生国家\n  nationality: string // 国籍\n}\n\nexport interface OtherName {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  type: 'maiden' | 'previous' | 'alias' // 娘家姓/曾用名/别名\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 2: 护照信息\n */\nexport interface Step2Data {\n  passportNumber: string // 护照号码\n  passportBookNumber?: string // 护照本编号（如有）\n  countryOfIssuance: string // 签发国家\n  cityOfIssuance: string // 签发城市\n  provinceOfIssuance: string // 签发省份\n  issuanceDate: string // 签发日期\n  expirationDate: string // 到期日期\n  \n  // 丢失/被盗护照\n  hasLostPassport: boolean\n  lostPassportDetails?: LostPassportDetail[]\n}\n\nexport interface LostPassportDetail {\n  passportNumber: string\n  countryOfIssuance: string\n  explanation: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 3: 联系方式\n */\nexport interface Step3Data {\n  // 地址信息\n  homeAddress: Address\n  mailingAddress?: Address // 邮寄地址（如不同）\n  sameAsHomeAddress: boolean\n  \n  // 联系方式\n  primaryPhone: string\n  secondaryPhone?: string\n  workPhone?: string\n  email: string\n  \n  // 高风险：社交媒体\n  hasSocialMedia: boolean\n  socialMediaAccounts?: SocialMediaAccount[]\n}\n\nexport interface Address {\n  street: string\n  street2?: string\n  city: string\n  province: string\n  postalCode: string\n  country: string\n}\n\nexport interface SocialMediaAccount {\n  platform: string // Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn等\n  handle: string // 账号名\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 4: 旅行信息\n */\nexport interface Step4Data {\n  purposeOfTrip: TripPurpose\n  otherPurpose?: string\n  \n  // 行程细节\n  arrivalDate?: string\n  departureDate?: string\n  stayDuration?: number // 天数\n  specificTravelPlans: boolean\n  travelItinerary?: string\n  \n  // 地址信息\n  usAddress?: Address\n  \n  // 费用支付\n  whoPayingForTrip: 'self' | 'company' | 'other-person' | 'other-organization'\n  payerDetails?: PayerDetails\n  \n  // 高风险：是否有美国联系人\n  hasUSContact: boolean\n}\n\nexport type TripPurpose = \n  | 'tourism'\n  | 'business'\n  | 'study'\n  | 'work'\n  | 'transit'\n  | 'medical'\n  | 'other'\n\nexport interface PayerDetails {\n  name?: string\n  phone?: string\n  email?: string\n  relationship?: string\n  address?: Address\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 5: 旅行伙伴\n */\nexport interface Step5Data {\n  travelingWithOthers: boolean\n  groupTravel: boolean\n  groupName?: string\n  companions?: Companion[]\n}\n\nexport interface Companion {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  relationship: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 6: 美国联系人\n */\nexport interface Step6Data {\n  hasUSContact: boolean\n  contacts?: USContact[]\n}\n\nexport interface USContact {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  organizationName?: string\n  relationship: string\n  address: Address\n  phone: string\n  email?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 7: 家庭信息\n */\nexport interface Step7Data {\n  // 父亲信息\n  father: ParentInfo\n  \n  // 母亲信息\n  mother: ParentInfo\n  \n  // 配偶信息（如已婚）\n  hasSpouse: boolean\n  spouse?: SpouseInfo\n  \n  // 高风险：家庭成员在美情况\n  hasImmediateFamilyInUS: boolean\n  familyInUS?: FamilyMemberInUS[]\n}\n\nexport interface ParentInfo {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  dateOfBirth: string\n  countryOfBirth?: string\n  currentLocation?: string\n  isInUS: boolean\n}\n\nexport interface SpouseInfo {\n  surname: string\n  givenName: string\n  dateOfBirth: string\n  nationality: string\n  placeOfBirth: string\n  countryOfBirth: string\n  address: Address\n}\n\nexport interface FamilyMemberInUS {\n  relationship: string\n  name: string\n  status: 'us-citizen' | 'permanent-resident' | 'other'\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 8: 工作/教育\n */\nexport interface Step8Data {\n  currentOccupation: OccupationType\n  \n  // 当前工作/学校\n  employerOrSchool?: EmployerInfo\n  \n  // 高风险：过往雇主（最近5年）\n  hasPreviousEmployment: boolean\n  previousEmployers?: EmployerInfo[]\n  \n  // 教育背景\n  education?: EducationInfo[]\n  \n  // 专业技能\n  hasSpecializedSkills: boolean\n  specializedSkills?: string[]\n}\n\nexport type OccupationType = \n  | 'employed'\n  | 'self-employed'\n  | 'student'\n  | 'retired'\n  | 'unemployed'\n  | 'other'\n\nexport interface EmployerInfo {\n  name: string\n  address: Address\n  phone?: string\n  position: string\n  duties?: string\n  supervisorName?: string\n  supervisorPhone?: string\n  startDate: string\n  endDate?: string\n  monthlySalary?: number\n}\n\nexport interface EducationInfo {\n  institutionName: string\n  address: Address\n  attendanceFrom: string\n  attendanceTo: string\n  degree?: string\n  fieldOfStudy?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 9: 安全问题(1) - 全部高风险\n */\nexport interface Step9Data {\n  // 健康相关\n  hasCommunicableDisease: boolean\n  communicableDiseaseDetails?: string\n  \n  hasMentalDisorder: boolean\n  mentalDisorderDetails?: string\n  \n  isDrugAbuser: boolean\n  drugAbuseDetails?: string\n  \n  // 犯罪记录\n  hasBeenArrested: boolean\n  arrestDetails?: string\n  \n  hasViolatedDrugLaw: boolean\n  drugLawViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 道德问题\n  hasEngagedInProstitution: boolean\n  hasEngagedInHumanTrafficking: boolean\n  hasAssistedInHumanTrafficking: boolean\n  \n  // 洗钱/金融犯罪\n  hasEngagedInMoneyLaundering: boolean\n  moneyLaunderingDetails?: string\n  \n  // 儿童监护\n  hasCommittedChildAbduction: boolean\n  childAbductionDetails?: string\n  \n  // 投票违规\n  hasVotedInViolation: boolean\n  votingViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 公民身份\n  hasRenouncecitizenshipForTax: boolean\n  citizenshipRenunciationDetails?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 10: 安全问题(2) - 全部高风险\n */\nexport interface Step10Data {\n  // 恐怖主义\n  hasEngagedInTerrorism: boolean\n  terrorismDetails?: string\n  \n  hasSupportedTerrorism: boolean\n  terrorismSupportDetails?: string\n  \n  isTerroristOrgMember: boolean\n  terroristOrgDetails?: string\n  \n  // 种族灭绝/酷刑\n  hasCommittedGenocide: boolean\n  genocideDetails?: string\n  \n  hasCommittedTorture: boolean\n  tortureDetails?: string\n  \n  hasCommittedExtrajudicialKilling: boolean\n  killingDetails?: string\n  \n  // 宗教自由\n  hasViolatedReligiousFreedom: boolean\n  religiousFreedomDetails?: string\n  \n  // 强制人口控制\n  hasCoercedTransplantation: boolean\n  transplantationDetails?: string\n  \n  // 签证/移民违规\n  hasBeenDeported: boolean\n  deportationDetails?: string\n  \n  hasViolatedImmigrationLaw: boolean\n  immigrationViolationDetails?: string\n  \n  hasWithheldChildCustody: boolean\n  childCustodyDetails?: string\n  \n  // 签证欺诈\n  hasUsedFraudulentVisa: boolean\n  fraudulentVisaDetails?: string\n  \n  // 非法居留\n  hasOverstayed: boolean\n  overstayDetails?: string\n  \n  // 其他\n  hasBeenDeniedVisa: boolean\n  visaDenialDetails?: string\n  \n  hasBeenDeniedEntry: boolean\n  entryDenialDetails?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 11: 以往旅行\n */\nexport interface Step11Data {\n  // 过去5年访美记录\n  hasVisitedUS: boolean\n  usVisits?: USVisit[]\n  \n  // 过去5年其他国家旅行\n  hasInternationalTravel: boolean\n  internationalTravels?: InternationalTravel[]\n  \n  // 驾照信息\n  hasDriverLicense: boolean\n  driverLicenses?: DriverLicense[]\n}\n\nexport interface USVisit {\n  arrivalDate: string\n  lengthOfStay: number // 天数\n}\n\nexport interface InternationalTravel {\n  country: string\n  arrivalDate: string\n  lengthOfStay: number\n}\n\nexport interface DriverLicense {\n  licenseNumber: string\n  state: string\n  country: string\n}\n\n/**\n * Step 12: 照片上传与确认\n */\nexport interface Step12Data {\n  // 照片信息\n  photo?: PhotoInfo\n  \n  // 确认声明\n  confirmations: {\n    informationAccurate: boolean\n    understandPenalties: boolean\n    agreeToTerms: boolean\n  }\n  \n  // 签名\n  signature?: string\n  signatureDate?: string\n}\n\nexport interface PhotoInfo {\n  filename: string\n  uploadDate: string\n  size: number\n  mimeType: string\n  dataUrl?: string // Base64编码的图片数据\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 表单校验相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 字段校验规则\n */\nexport interface ValidationRule {\n  required?: boolean\n  pattern?: RegExp\n  minLength?: number\n  maxLength?: number\n  min?: number\n  max?: number\n  custom?: (value: any) => boolean | string\n}\n\n/**\n * 字段校验结果\n */\nexport interface ValidationResult {\n  valid: boolean\n  errors: string[]\n}\n\n/**\n * 步骤校验结果\n */\nexport interface StepValidation {\n  step: number\n  valid: boolean\n  errors: Record<string, string[]>\n  warnings: Record<string, string[]>\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// UI相关类型\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 步骤信息\n */\nexport interface StepInfo {\n  number: number\n  title: string\n  description: string\n  icon: string\n  completed: boolean\n  hasWarnings: boolean\n}\n\n/**\n * Toast通知类型\n */\nexport type ToastType = 'success' | 'error' | 'warning' | 'info'\n\nexport interface Toast {\n  id: string\n  type: ToastType\n  message: string\n  duration?: number\n}\n\n/**\n * Modal配置\n */\nexport interface ModalConfig {\n  title: string\n  message: string\n  confirmText?: string\n  cancelText?: string\n  type?: 'info' | 'warning' | 'danger'\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 套餐相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 套餐类型\n */\nexport type PlanType = 'free' | 'personal' | 'family'\n\n/**\n * 套餐信息\n */\nexport interface Plan {\n  id: PlanType\n  name: string\n  price: number\n  syncLimit: number | null // null表示无限制\n  features: string[]\n  popular?: boolean\n}\n\n// ============================================\n// 同步相关\n// ============================================\n\n/**\n * 同步记录\n */\nexport interface SyncRecord {\n  id: string\n  draftId: string\n  timestamp: Date\n  success: boolean\n  errorMessage?: string\n}\n\n/**\n * 同步状态\n */\nexport interface SyncStatus {\n  syncing: boolean\n  lastSyncTime?: Date\n  error?: string\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第二批文件：布局和营销页面\n\n### 7. layouts/default.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\">\n    <!-- 顶部导航 -->\n    <header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\">\n      <nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center h-16\">\n          <!-- Logo -->\n          <NuxtLink to=\"/\" class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n            <Icon name=\"mdi:passport\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600\" />\n            <span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">DS-160 Helper</span>\n          </NuxtLink>\n\n          <!-- 桌面端导航 -->\n          <div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8\">\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/features\"\n              class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors\"\n            >\n              功能介绍\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/pricing\"\n              class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors\"\n            >\n              定价\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n              class=\"btn-primary\"\n            >\n              开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 移动端菜单按钮 -->\n          <button\n            @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = !mobileMenuOpen\"\n            class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100\"\n          >\n            <Icon\n              :name=\"mobileMenuOpen ? 'mdi:close' : 'mdi:menu'\"\n              class=\"w-6 h-6\"\n            />\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 移动端菜单 -->\n        <Transition\n          enter-active-class=\"transition duration-200 ease-out\"\n          enter-from-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n          enter-to-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n          leave-active-class=\"transition duration-100 ease-in\"\n          leave-from-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n          leave-to-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n        >\n          <div v-if=\"mobileMenuOpen\" class=\"md:hidden py-4 space-y-2\">\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/features\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              功能介绍\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/pricing\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              定价\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink\n              to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n              class=\"block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg text-center\"\n              @click=\"mobileMenuOpen = false\"\n            >\n              开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n        </Transition>\n      </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"flex-1\">\n      <slot />\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-300\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\">\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n          <!-- 公司信息 -->\n          <div class=\"col-span-1 md:col-span-2\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:passport\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-400\" />\n              <span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">DS-160 Helper</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4\">\n              简化DS-160表单填写流程，让签证申请更轻松。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">\n              © 2024 DS-160 Helper. All rights reserved.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 产品 -->\n          <div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">产品</h3>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/features\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  功能介绍\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/pricing\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  定价方案\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <NuxtLink to=\"/app/dashboard\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                  开始使用\n                </NuxtLink>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          <!-- 支持 -->\n          <div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">支持</h3>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">帮助中心</a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">隐私政策</a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">服务条款</a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nconst mobileMenuOpen = ref(false)\n\n// 关闭移动菜单（路由变化时）\nconst route = useRoute()\nwatch(() => route.path, () => {\n  mobileMenuOpen.value = false\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 8. layouts/app.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\">\n    <!-- 顶部导航栏 -->\n    <AppHeader />\n\n    <div class=\"flex\">\n      <!-- 左侧步骤导航 -->\n      <aside\n        class=\"hidden lg:block w-64 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] sticky top-16\"\n      >\n        <StepNavigation />\n      </aside>\n\n      <!-- 主内容区域 -->\n      <main class=\"flex-1 p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n          <slot />\n        </div>\n      </main>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 移动端步骤导航（底部） -->\n    <div class=\"lg:hidden fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white border-t border-gray-200 z-40\">\n      <MobileStepNavigation />\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Toast通知 -->\n    <ToastContainer />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\n// 确保在应用布局中初始化必要的stores\nconst draftStore = useDraftStore()\nconst formStore = useFormStore()\n\n// 页面加载时初始化\nonMounted(() => {\n  draftStore.loadDrafts()\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 9. pages/index.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <!-- Hero Section -->\n    <section class=\"relative bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 text-white overflow-hidden\">\n      <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-grid-white/[0.05] bg-[size:20px_20px]\" />\n      <div class=\"relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28\">\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\n          <h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in\">\n            DS-160 表单填写\n            <br />\n            <span class=\"text-primary-200\">从未如此简单</span>\n          </h1>\n          <p class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up\">\n            智能引导 · 高风险提示 · 自动保存草稿\n            <br />\n            让美国签证申请不再令人头疼\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-slide-up\">\n            <NuxtLink to=\"/app/dashboard\" class=\"btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:rocket-launch\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n              免费开始使用\n            </NuxtLink>\n            <NuxtLink to=\"/features\" class=\"btn bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n              <Icon name=\"mdi:information\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n              了解更多\n            </NuxtLink>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 核心卖点 -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-white\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n            为什么选择 DS-160 Helper？\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n            专为中国申请者设计，解决DS-160表单填写的所有痛点\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:list-box-outline\"\n            title=\"12步智能引导\"\n            description=\"复杂表单拆解为清晰步骤，每步都有中文说明和填写建议\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:alert-circle\"\n            title=\"高风险字段提示\"\n            description=\"自动识别敏感问题，橙色警告框+专业建议，避免拒签风险\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:content-save-outline\"\n            title=\"自动保存草稿\"\n            description=\"实时保存到本地，随时暂停随时继续，永不丢失数据\"\n          />\n          <FeatureCard\n            icon=\"mdi:sync\"\n            title=\"一键同步DS-160\"\n            description=\"填写完成后，一键同步到官方网站，节省80%时间\"\n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 工作流程 -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-gray-50\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n            三步完成DS-160\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600\">\n            简单、快速、安全\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n          <ProcessStep\n            number=\"1\"\n            title=\"创建草稿\"\n            description=\"点击开始，创建您的DS-160草稿，所有数据本地保存\"\n            icon=\"mdi:file-document-edit-outline\"\n          />\n          <ProcessStep\n            number=\"2\"\n            title=\"填写表单\"\n            description=\"按照12个步骤填写，每个字段都有详细说明和示例\"\n            icon=\"mdi:form-textbox\"\n          />\n          <ProcessStep\n            number=\"3\"\n            title=\"同步提交\"\n            description=\"检查确认后，一键同步到DS-160官网，完成申请\"\n            icon=\"mdi:cloud-upload-outline\"\n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 用户评价 -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-white\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n            用户真实反馈\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600\">\n            已帮助 10,000+ 用户成功填写DS-160\n          \n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: QAEngineer\n\nQAEngineer (to chat_manager):\n\n我将继续完成代码生成。由于输出长度限制，我会分批完成剩余文件。\n\n---\n\n## 继续第二批文件\n\n### 9. pages/index.vue (续)\n\n```vue\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n          <TestimonialCard\n            name=\"张女士\"\n            role=\"旅游签证申请者\"\n            content=\"第一次申请美国签证，原本很担心填错表格。用了DS-160 Helper后，每个问题都有清晰的中文说明，高风险字段还有特别提示，最后顺利拿到签证！\"\n            avatar=\"👩\"\n          />\n          <TestimonialCard\n            name=\"李先生\"\n            role=\"商务签证申请者\"\n            content=\"工作忙没时间一次性填完，草稿自动保存功能太实用了。而且12步骤设计很合理，不会感到overwhelmed。强烈推荐！\"\n            avatar=\"👨\"\n          />\n          <TestimonialCard\n            name=\"王同学\"\n            role=\"F1学生签证申请者\"\n            content=\"安全问题部分最让人头疼，但Helper的警告提示和填写建议让我知道哪些问题需要特别注意。感觉比自己摸索省了好几个小时。\"\n            avatar=\"🎓\"\n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- CTA Section -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-primary-600 text-white\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6\">\n          准备好开始您的签证申请了吗？\n        </h2>\n        <p class=\"text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8\">\n          免费版提供完整功能，无需注册即可使用\n        </p>\n        <NuxtLink\n          to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n          class=\"btn bg-white text-primary-600 hover:bg-gray-100 text-lg px-8 py-3 inline-block\"\n        >\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:arrow-right\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n          立即开始填写\n        </NuxtLink>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\n// SEO优化\nuseHead({\n  title: 'DS-160 Helper - 美国签证申请表辅助填写工具',\n  meta: [\n    {\n      name: 'description',\n      content: '简化DS-160表单填写流程，智能引导12个步骤，高风险字段自动提示，草稿自动保存。让美国签证申请更轻松、更安全。'\n    },\n    {\n      property: 'og:title',\n      content: 'DS-160 Helper - 美国签证申请表辅助工具'\n    },\n    {\n      property: 'og:description',\n      content: '智能引导 · 高风险提示 · 自动保存草稿 - 让DS-160填写不再令人头疼'\n    }\n  ]\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 10. pages/features.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"py-12 sm:py-16\">\n    <!-- 页面头部 -->\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-16\">\n      <div class=\"text-center\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n          强大功能，简化流程\n        </h1>\n        <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n          DS-160 Helper 提供全方位的表单填写辅助功能，\n          从智能引导到风险提示，让签证申请变得简单安全\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 核心功能详解 -->\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20\">\n      <div class=\"space-y-20\">\n        <!-- 功能1：12步智能引导 -->\n        <FeatureDetail\n          :reverse=\"false\"\n          icon=\"mdi:format-list-numbered\"\n          title=\"12步智能引导系统\"\n          description=\"我们将复杂的DS-160表单拆解为12个清晰的步骤，每个步骤聚焦特定主题，避免信息过载。\"\n        >\n          <template #content>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-600\">\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:check-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n                <span><strong>Step 1-3:</strong> 个人基本信息、护照信息、联系方式</span>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:check-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n                <span><strong>Step 4-6:</strong> 旅行计划、同行人员、美国联系人</span>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:check-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n                <span><strong>Step 7-8:</strong> 家庭信息、工作/教育背景</span>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:check-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n                <span><strong>Step 9-10:</strong> 安全问题（健康、犯罪、恐怖主义等）</span>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:check-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n                <span><strong>Step 11-12:</strong> 以往旅行记录、照片上传与最终确认</span>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </template>\n        </FeatureDetail>\n\n        <!-- 功能2：高风险字段提示 -->\n        <FeatureDetail\n          :reverse=\"true\"\n          icon=\"mdi:alert-circle-outline\"\n          title=\"高风险字段智能提示\"\n          description=\"自动识别可能影响签证结果的敏感问题，用橙色警告框标注，并提供专业的填写建议。\"\n        >\n          <template #content>\n            <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n              <div class=\"bg-warning-50 border-l-4 border-warning-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                  <Icon name=\"mdi:alert\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-warning-600 mr-2 mt-0.5\" />\n                  <div>\n                    <p class=\"font-semibold text-warning-900 mb-1\">高风险字段示例</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-warning-800\">\n                      \"是否有曾用名或别名？\" - 如果有，必须如实填写并提供证明文件。\n                      隐瞒信息可能导致永久拒签。\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm\">\n                <li>✓ 曾用名/别名信息</li>\n                <li>✓ 社交媒体账号</li>\n                <li>✓ 家庭成员在美情况</li>\n                <li>✓ 所有安全问题（Step 9-10）</li>\n                <li>✓ 签证拒签史/非法滞留史</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </template>\n        </FeatureDetail>\n\n        <!-- 功能3：自动保存草稿 -->\n        <FeatureDetail\n          :reverse=\"false\"\n          icon=\"mdi:content-save-auto-outline\"\n          title=\"自动保存草稿功能\"\n          description=\"每次输入后自动保存到浏览器本地存储，即使关闭浏览器也不会丢失数据。\"\n        >\n          <template #content>\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n              <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:shield-check\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-2\" />\n                <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1\">数据安全</h4>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                  所有数据仅保存在您的设备上，不会上传到任何服务器\n                </p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:clock-outline\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-2\" />\n                <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1\">随时继续</h4>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                  可以分多次完成填写，系统会记住您的进度\n                </p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:file-multiple-outline\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-2\" />\n                <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1\">多草稿管理</h4>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                  可以创建多个草稿，方便为家人朋友准备申请\n                </p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:backup-restore\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600 mb-2\" />\n                <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1\">一键恢复</h4>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                  可以随时查看和恢复之前保存的草稿\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </template>\n        </FeatureDetail>\n\n        <!-- 功能4：实时表单校验 -->\n        <FeatureDetail\n          :reverse=\"true\"\n          icon=\"mdi:check-decagram\"\n          title=\"实时表单校验\"\n          description=\"输入时即时检查格式和逻辑错误，确保提交前所有信息都符合要求。\"\n        >\n          <template #content>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-600\">\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:checkbox-marked-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5\" />\n                <span>必填字段检查：确保所有必填信息都已填写</span>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:checkbox-marked-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5\" />\n                <span>格式验证：电话、邮箱、护照号等自动检查格式</span>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:checkbox-marked-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5\" />\n                <span>逻辑验证：日期前后关系、年龄计算等逻辑检查</span>\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                <Icon name=\"mdi:checkbox-marked-circle\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5\" />\n                <span>完整性检查：步骤完成度实时显示</span>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </template>\n        </FeatureDetail>\n\n        <!-- 功能5：中英文双语支持 -->\n        <FeatureDetail\n          :reverse=\"false\"\n          icon=\"mdi:translate\"\n          title=\"中英文双语支持\"\n          description=\"每个字段都提供中文说明和英文填写示例，帮助您准确理解问题含义。\"\n        >\n          <template #content>\n            <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg\">\n              <div class=\"mb-4\">\n                <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">\n                  Given Name (名) *\n                </label>\n                <input\n                  type=\"text\"\n                  placeholder=\"例如：MING\"\n                  class=\"form-input\"\n                  disabled\n                />\n                <p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                  💡 <strong>填写说明：</strong>填写护照上的名字拼音（全大写）。\n                  例如：\"李明\" 应填写 \"MING\"\n                </p>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 italic\">\n                * 所有字段都有类似的中文说明和填写示例\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </template>\n        </FeatureDetail>\n\n        <!-- 功能6：进度追踪 -->\n        <FeatureDetail\n          :reverse=\"true\"\n          icon=\"mdi:progress-check\"\n          title=\"可视化进度追踪\"\n          description=\"清晰显示整体进度和每个步骤的完成状态，让您随时了解还需完成哪些内容。\"\n        >\n          <template #content>\n            <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n              <!-- 进度条示例 -->\n              <div>\n                <div class=\"flex justify-between text-sm mb-2\">\n                  <span class=\"text-gray-600\">整体进度</span>\n                  <span class=\"font-semibold text-primary-600\">8/12 步骤完成</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-3\">\n                  <div class=\"bg-primary-600 h-3 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 67%\"></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              \n              <!-- 步骤列表示例 -->\n              <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-2 text-sm\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-center text-green-600\">\n                  <Icon name=\"mdi:check-circle\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" />\n                  <span>Step 1 ✓</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-center text-green-600\">\n                  <Icon name=\"mdi:check-circle\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" />\n                  <span>Step 2 ✓</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-center text-primary-600\">\n                  <Icon name=\"mdi:pencil-circle\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" />\n                  <span>Step 3 ⏳</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-center text-gray-400\">\n                  <Icon name=\"mdi:circle-outline\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-1\" />\n                  <span>Step 4</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </template>\n        </FeatureDetail>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CTA -->\n    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 py-16\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n          准备好体验这些强大功能了吗？\n        </h2>\n        <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8\">\n          免费版即可使用所有核心功能\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\">\n          <NuxtLink to=\"/app/dashboard\" class=\"btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n            立即开始使用\n          </NuxtLink>\n          <NuxtLink to=\"/pricing\" class=\"btn-outline text-lg px-8 py-3\">\n            查看定价方案\n          </NuxtLink>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nuseHead({\n  title: '功能介绍 - DS-160 Helper',\n  meta: [\n    {\n      name: 'description',\n      content: 'DS-160 Helper提供12步智能引导、高风险字段提示、自动保存草稿等强大功能，让美国签证申请更简单安全。'\n    }\n  ]\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 11. pages/pricing.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"py-12 sm:py-16\">\n    <!-- 页面头部 -->\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-16 text-center\">\n      <h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n        简单透明的定价\n      </h1>\n      <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n        选择适合您的方案，所有套餐都包含核心功能\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 定价卡片 -->\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n        <!-- 免费版 -->\n        <PricingCard\n          plan=\"free\"\n          name=\"免费版\"\n          :price=\"0\"\n          period=\"永久免费\"\n          description=\"适合个人用户尝试\"\n          :features=\"[\n            '12步智能引导',\n            '高风险字段提示',\n            '自动保存草稿',\n            '实时表单校验',\n            '中文填写说明',\n            '3次DS-160同步'\n          ]\"\n          :limitations=\"[\n            '仅限3次同步到DS-160官网'\n          ]\"\n          cta-text=\"免费开始\"\n          cta-link=\"/app/dashboard\"\n        />\n\n        <!-- 个人版 -->\n        <PricingCard\n          plan=\"personal\"\n          name=\"个人版\"\n          :price=\"29\"\n          period=\"一次性付费\"\n          description=\"适合单次申请用户\"\n          :features=\"[\n            '✓ 免费版所有功能',\n            '无限次DS-160同步',\n            '优先技术支持',\n            '表单数据导出',\n            '填写进度云备份',\n            '12个月有效期'\n          ]\"\n          :popular=\"true\"\n          cta-text=\"立即购买\"\n          cta-link=\"/app/dashboard\"\n        />\n\n        <!-- 家庭版 -->\n        <PricingCard\n          plan=\"family\"\n          name=\"家庭版\"\n          :price=\"79\"\n          period=\"一次性付费\"\n          description=\"适合家庭或团队\"\n          :features=\"[\n            '✓ 个人版所有功能',\n            '支持5个账号',\n            '共享草稿模板',\n            '批量导出功能',\n            '专属客服支持',\n            '24个月有效期'\n          ]\"\n          cta-text=\"立即购买\"\n          cta-link=\"/app/dashboard\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 功能对比表 -->\n    <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center\">\n        详细功能对比\n      </h2>\n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden\">\n        <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n          <table class=\"w-full\">\n            <thead class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n              <tr>\n                <th class=\"px-6 py-4 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900\">\n                  功能特性\n                </th>\n                <th class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900\">\n                  免费版\n                </th>\n                <th class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 bg-primary-50\">\n                  个人版\n                </th>\n                <th class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900\">\n                  家庭版\n                </th>\n              </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody class=\"divide-y divide-gray-200\">\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"12步智能引导\"\n                :free=\"true\"\n                :personal=\"true\"\n                :family=\"true\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"高风险字段提示\"\n                :free=\"true\"\n                :personal=\"true\"\n                :family=\"true\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"自动保存草稿\"\n                :free=\"true\"\n                :personal=\"true\"\n                :family=\"true\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"实时表单校验\"\n                :free=\"true\"\n                :personal=\"true\"\n                :family=\"true\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"DS-160同步次数\"\n                free=\"3次\"\n                personal=\"无限\"\n                family=\"无限\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"支持账号数\"\n                free=\"1个\"\n                personal=\"1个\"\n                family=\"5个\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"数据云备份\"\n                :free=\"false\"\n                :personal=\"true\"\n                :family=\"true\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"表单数据导出\"\n                :free=\"false\"\n                :personal=\"true\"\n                :family=\"true\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"共享草稿模板\"\n                :free=\"false\"\n                :personal=\"false\"\n                :family=\"true\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"技术支持\"\n                free=\"社区\"\n                personal=\"优先\"\n                family=\"专属\"\n              />\n              <ComparisonRow\n                feature=\"有效期\"\n                free=\"永久\"\n                personal=\"12个月\"\n                family=\"24个月\"\n              />\n            </tbody>\n          </table>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- FAQ -->\n    <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center\">\n        常见问题\n      </h2>\n      \n      <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n        <FAQItem\n          question=\"什么是DS-160同步？\"\n          answer=\"DS-160同步是指将您在我们平台填写的表单数据，自动填充到美国国务院的官方DS-160网站。这可以节省您大量的重复输入时间。免费版提供3次同步机会，足够完成一次申请（包括测试和正式提交）。\"\n        />\n        <FAQItem\n          question=\"我的数据安全吗？\"\n          answer=\"非常安全。免费版的所有数据都保存在您的浏览器本地存储中，不会上传到任何服务器。付费版提供可选的云备份功能，数据采用银行级加密传输和存储。\"\n        />\n        <FAQItem\n          question=\"购买后如何使用？\"\n          answer=\"购买成功后，您会收到一个激活码。在应用中输入激活码即可升级到对应套餐。所有功能立即生效。\"\n        />\n        <FAQItem\n          question=\"可以退款吗？\"\n          answer=\"如果您在购买后7天内未使用任何付费功能，可以申请全额退款。使用后不支持退款，但我们提供免费版供您充分试用。\"\n        />\n        <FAQItem\n          question=\"家庭版的5个账号是什么意思？\"\n          answer=\"家庭版允许您为最多5个人创建独立账号，每个人都有自己的草稿和数据。这非常适合全家一起申请签证，或者帮助朋友填写表单。\"\n        />\n        <FAQItem\n          question=\"有效期到期后会怎样？\"\n          answer=\"有效期到期后，您仍然可以查看和导出之前保存的数据，但无法使用DS-160同步功能。您可以选择续费来继续使用所有功能。\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CTA -->\n    <div class=\"bg-primary-600 py-16\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">\n          还在犹豫？先试试免费版！\n        </h2>\n        <p class=\"text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8\">\n          免费版包含所有核心功能，无需信用卡，立即开始使用\n        </p>\n        <NuxtLink\n          to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n          class=\"btn bg-white text-primary-600 hover:bg-gray-100 text-lg px-8 py-3 inline-block\"\n        >\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:rocket-launch\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2 inline\" />\n          免费开始使用\n        </NuxtLink>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nuseHead({\n  title: '定价方案 - DS-160 Helper',\n  meta: [\n    {\n      name: 'description',\n      content: 'DS-160 Helper提供免费版、个人版和家庭版三种方案。免费版永久免费，付费版提供无限同步和更多高级功能。'\n    }\n  ]\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n由于输出长度限制，我需要继续在下一个回复中完成组件文件。让我继续生成营销页面的组件。\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: DevOpsEngineer\n\nDevOpsEngineer (to chat_manager):\n\n我将继续生成营销页面所需的组件文件。\n\n---\n\n## 营销页面组件\n\n### 12. components/marketing/FeatureCard.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg mb-4\">\n      <Icon :name=\"icon\" class=\"w-6 h-6 text-primary-600\" />\n    </div>\n    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">\n      {{ title }}\n    </h3>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-600\">\n      {{ description }}\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps<{\n  icon: string\n  title: string\n  description: string\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 13. components/marketing/ProcessStep.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"relative\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center text-center\">\n      <!-- 步骤编号 -->\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full text-2xl font-bold mb-4 shadow-lg\">\n        {{ number }}\n      </div>\n      \n      <!-- 图标 -->\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-primary-50 rounded-full mb-4\">\n        <Icon :name=\"icon\" class=\"w-10 h-10 text-primary-600\" />\n      </div>\n      \n      <!-- 标题和描述 -->\n      <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">\n        {{ title }}\n      </h3>\n      <p class=\"text-gray-600\">\n        {{ description }}\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 连接线（仅在非最后一个步骤显示） -->\n    <div\n      v-if=\"number !== '3'\"\n      class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-8 left-1/2 w-full h-0.5 bg-primary-200\"\n      style=\"transform: translateX(50%)\"\n    />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps<{\n  number: string\n  title: string\n  description: string\n  icon: string\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 14. components/marketing/TestimonialCard.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center mb-4\">\n      <div class=\"text-4xl mr-3\">{{ avatar }}</div>\n      <div>\n        <h4 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">{{ name }}</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">{{ role }}</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-gray-700 italic\">\n      \"{{ content }}\"\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"flex mt-4\">\n      <Icon\n        v-for=\"i in 5\"\n        :key=\"i\"\n        name=\"mdi:star\"\n        class=\"w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400\"\n      />\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps<{\n  name: string\n  role: string\n  content: string\n  avatar: string\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 15. components/marketing/FeatureDetail.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\" :class=\"{ 'lg:flex-row-reverse': reverse }\">\n    <!-- 图标和标题 -->\n    <div :class=\"{ 'lg:order-2': reverse }\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl mb-6\">\n        <Icon :name=\"icon\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-primary-600\" />\n      </div>\n      <h3 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">\n        {{ title }}\n      </h3>\n      <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6\">\n        {{ description }}\n      </p>\n      <slot name=\"content\" />\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 占位图（实际项目中可以替换为真实截图） -->\n    <div :class=\"{ 'lg:order-1': reverse }\">\n      <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 rounded-xl p-8 aspect-video flex items-center justify-center\">\n        <Icon :name=\"icon\" class=\"w-32 h-32 text-primary-400 opacity-50\" />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps<{\n  icon: string\n  title: string\n  description: string\n  reverse: boolean\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 16. components/marketing/PricingCard.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div\n    class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl\"\n    :class=\"{\n      'border-primary-500 ring-4 ring-primary-100': popular,\n      'border-gray-200': !popular\n    }\"\n  >\n    <!-- 热门标签 -->\n    <div v-if=\"popular\" class=\"bg-primary-600 text-white text-center py-2 text-sm font-semibold\">\n      🔥 最受欢迎\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"p-8\">\n      <!-- 套餐名称 -->\n      <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">\n        {{ name }}\n      </h3>\n      \n      <!-- 价格 -->\n      <div class=\"mb-4\">\n        <span class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900\">\n          {{ price === 0 ? '免费' : `¥${price}` }}\n        </span>\n        <span class=\"text-gray-600 ml-2\">{{ period }}</span>\n      </div>\n      \n      <!-- 描述 -->\n      <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">\n        {{ description }}\n      </p>\n      \n      <!-- CTA按钮 -->\n      <NuxtLink\n        :to=\"ctaLink\"\n        class=\"block w-full text-center py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 mb-6\"\n        :class=\"\n          popular\n            ? 'bg-primary-600 text-white hover:bg-primary-700'\n            : 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-200'\n        \"\n      >\n        {{ ctaText }}\n      </NuxtLink>\n      \n      <!-- 功能列表 -->\n      <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n        <div\n          v-for=\"(feature, index) in features\"\n          :key=\"index\"\n          class=\"flex items-start\"\n        >\n          <Icon\n            name=\"mdi:check-circle\"\n            class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\"\n          />\n          <span class=\"text-gray-700\">{{ feature }}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <!-- 限制说明 -->\n      <div v-if=\"limitations && limitations.length > 0\" class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200\">\n        <div\n          v-for=\"(limitation, index) in limitations\"\n          :key=\"index\"\n          class=\"flex items-start text-sm text-gray-500\"\n        >\n          <Icon\n            name=\"mdi:information-outline\"\n            class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\"\n          />\n          <span>{{ limitation }}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport type { PlanType } from '~/types'\n\ndefineProps<{\n  plan: PlanType\n  name: string\n  price: number\n  period: string\n  description: string\n  features: string[]\n  limitations?: string[]\n  popular?: boolean\n  ctaText: string\n  ctaLink: string\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 17. components/marketing/ComparisonRow.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <tr class=\"hover:bg-gray-50\">\n    <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-900\">\n      {{ feature }}\n    </td>\n    <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\">\n      <ComparisonCell :value=\"free\" />\n    </td>\n    <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center bg-primary-50/50\">\n      <ComparisonCell :value=\"personal\" />\n    </td>\n    <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\">\n      <ComparisonCell :value=\"family\" />\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps<{\n  feature: string\n  free: boolean | string\n  personal: boolean | string\n  family: boolean | string\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 18. components/marketing/ComparisonCell.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <Icon\n      v-if=\"value === true\"\n      name=\"mdi:check\"\n      class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto\"\n    />\n    <Icon\n      v-else-if=\"value === false\"\n      name=\"mdi:close\"\n      class=\"w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto\"\n    />\n    <span v-else class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">\n      {{ value }}\n    </span>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps<{\n  value: boolean | string\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 19. components/marketing/FAQItem.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden\">\n    <button\n      class=\"w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors\"\n      @click=\"isOpen = !isOpen\"\n    >\n      <span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">{{ question }}</span>\n      <Icon\n        :name=\"isOpen ? 'mdi:chevron-up' : 'mdi:chevron-down'\"\n        class=\"w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 flex-shrink-0\"\n      />\n    </button>\n    \n    <Transition\n      enter-active-class=\"transition-all duration-200 ease-out\"\n      enter-from-class=\"max-h-0 opacity-0\"\n      enter-to-class=\"max-h-96 opacity-100\"\n      leave-active-class=\"transition-all duration-200 ease-in\"\n      leave-from-class=\"max-h-96 opacity-100\"\n      leave-to-class=\"max-h-0 opacity-0\"\n    >\n      <div v-if=\"isOpen\" class=\"px-6 pb-4 text-gray-600\">\n        {{ answer }}\n      </div>\n    </Transition>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps<{\n  question: string\n  answer: string\n}>()\n\nconst isOpen = ref(false)\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n现在让我继续生成应用页面的组件和Pinia stores。\n\n### 20. components/app/AppHeader.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50 h-16\">\n    <div class=\"h-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex items-center justify-between\">\n      <!-- Logo和返回首页 -->\n      <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\">\n        <NuxtLink to=\"/\" class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\">\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:passport\" class=\"w-6 h-6 text-primary-600\" />\n          <span class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 hidden sm:inline\">DS-160 Helper</span>\n        </NuxtLink>\n        \n        <!-- 当前草稿信息 -->\n        <div v-if=\"currentDraft\" class=\"hidden md:flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600\">\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:file-document-outline\" class=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n          <span>草稿 #{{ currentDraft.id.slice(0, 8) }}</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-400\">|</span>\n          <span>步骤 {{ currentDraft.currentStep }}/12</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- 右侧操作 -->\n      <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3\">\n        <!-- 自动保存状态 -->\n        <div class=\"hidden sm:flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-500\">\n          <Icon\n            :name=\"isSaving ? 'mdi:loading' : 'mdi:check-circle'\"\n            class=\"w-4 h-4\"\n            :class=\"{ 'animate-spin': isSaving, 'text-green-500': !isSaving }\"\n          />\n          <span>{{ isSaving ? '保存中...' : '已保存' }}</span>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 同步次数 -->\n        <div\n          v-if=\"currentDraft\"\n          class=\"flex items-center space-x-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg text-sm\"\n        >\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:sync\" class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-600\" />\n          <span class=\"text-gray-700\">{{ syncCount }}/{{ syncLimit }}</span>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 菜单按钮 -->\n        <button\n          @click=\"showMenu = !showMenu\"\n          class=\"p-2 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg transition-colors\"\n        >\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:dots-vertical\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-gray-600\" />\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 下拉菜单 -->\n    <Transition\n      enter-active-class=\"transition duration-100 ease-out\"\n      enter-from-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n      enter-to-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n      leave-active-class=\"transition duration-75 ease-in\"\n      leave-from-class=\"transform scale-100 opacity-100\"\n      leave-to-class=\"transform scale-95 opacity-0\"\n    >\n      <div\n        v-if=\"showMenu\"\n        class=\"absolute right-4 top-14 w-56 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gray-200 py-2 z-50\"\n      >\n        <NuxtLink\n          to=\"/app/dashboard\"\n          class=\"flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100\"\n          @click=\"showMenu = false\"\n        >\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:view-dashboard\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n          返回面板\n        </NuxtLink>\n        <NuxtLink\n          to=\"/app/drafts\"\n          class=\"flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100\"\n          @click=\"showMenu = false\"\n        >\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:file-multiple\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n          草稿管理\n        </NuxtLink>\n        <div class=\"border-t border-gray-200 my-2\"></div>\n        <button\n          class=\"flex items-center w-full px-4 py-2 text-sm text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50\"\n          @click=\"handleNewDraft\"\n        >\n          <Icon name=\"mdi:plus-circle\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n          创建新草稿\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </Transition>\n  </header>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nconst draftStore = useDraftStore()\nconst syncStore = useSyncStore()\n\nconst showMenu = ref(false)\n\nconst currentDraft = computed(() => draftStore.currentDraft)\nconst isSaving = computed(() => draftStore.isSaving)\nconst syncCount = computed(() => currentDraft.value?.syncCount || 0)\nconst syncLimit = computed(() => syncStore.syncLimit)\n\nconst handleNewDraft = () => {\n  showMenu.value = false\n  // 确认对话框\n  if (confirm('创建新草稿将保存当前进度。确定要创建新草稿吗？')) {\n    draftStore.createDraft()\n    navigateTo('/app/dashboard')\n  }\n}\n\n// 点击外部关闭菜单\nonClickOutside(showMenu, () => {\n  showMenu.value = false\n})\n</script>\n```\n\n### 21. components/app/StepNavigation.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <nav class=\"py-6 px-4 h-full overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar\">\n    <!-- 进度概览 -->\n    <div class=\"mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex justify-between text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n        <span>整体进度</span>\n        <span class=\"font-semibold text-primary-600\">{{ completedSteps }}/12</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-2\">\n        <div\n          class=\"bg-primary-600 h-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-300\"\n          :style=\"{ width: `${(completedSteps / 12) * 100}%` }\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 步骤列表 -->\n    <div class=\"space-y-2\">\n      <StepItem\n        v-for=\"step in steps\"\n        :key=\"step.number\"\n        :step=\"step\"\n        :is-current=\"step.number === currentStep\"\n        :is-completed=\"step.completed\"\n        @click=\"navigateToStep(step.number)\"\n      />\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 底部操作 -->\n    <div class=\"mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200\">\n      <button\n        v-if=\"allStepsCompleted\"\n        class=\"w-full btn-primary mb-3\"\n        @click=\"handleSync\"\n      >\n        <Icon name=\"mdi:sync\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2 inline\" />\n        同步到DS-160\n      </button>\n      <button\n        class=\"w-full btn-secondary text-sm\"\n        @click=\"handleSaveDraft\"\n      >\n        <Icon name=\"mdi:content-save\" class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2 inline\" />\n        保存草稿\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport type { StepInfo } from '~/types'\n\nconst formStore = useFormStore()\nconst draftStore = useDraftStore()\nconst syncStore = useSyncStore()\nconst router = useRouter()\n\nconst currentStep = computed(() => formStore.currentStep)\nconst completedSteps = computed(() => formStore.completedSteps.length)\nconst allStepsCompleted = computed(() => completedSteps.value === 12)\n\nconst steps = computed<StepInfo[]>(() => [\n  {\n    number: 1,\n    title: '个人信息',\n    description: '基本信息和曾用名',\n    icon: 'mdi:account',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(1),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(1)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 2,\n    title: '护照信息',\n    description: '护照号码和签发信息',\n    icon: 'mdi:passport',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(2),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(2)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 3,\n    title: '联系方式',\n    description: '地址、电话和社交媒体',\n    icon: 'mdi:email',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(3),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(3)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 4,\n    title: '旅行信息',\n    description: '旅行目的和计划',\n    icon: 'mdi:airplane',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(4),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(4)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 5,\n    title: '旅行伙伴',\n    description: '同行人员信息',\n    icon: 'mdi:account-group',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(5),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(5)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 6,\n    title: '美国联系人',\n    description: '在美联系人信息',\n    icon: 'mdi:account-tie',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(6),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(6)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 7,\n    title: '家庭信息',\n    description: '父母、配偶信息',\n    icon: 'mdi:home-heart',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(7),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(7)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 8,\n    title: '工作/教育',\n    description: '职业和教育背景',\n    icon: 'mdi:briefcase',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(8),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(8)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 9,\n    title: '安全问题(1)',\n    description: '健康和犯罪记录',\n    icon: 'mdi:shield-alert',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(9),\n    hasWarnings: true // 所有安全问题都是高风险\n  },\n  {\n    number: 10,\n    title: '安全问题(2)',\n    description: '恐怖主义和签证历史',\n    icon: 'mdi:shield-alert',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(10),\n    hasWarnings: true\n  },\n  {\n    number: 11,\n    title: '以往旅行',\n    description: '旅行和驾照记录',\n    icon: 'mdi:earth',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(11),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(11)\n  },\n  {\n    number: 12,\n    title: '照片与确认',\n    description: '上传照片并确认',\n    icon: 'mdi:camera',\n    completed: formStore.isStepCompleted(12),\n    hasWarnings: formStore.hasStepWarnings(12)\n  }\n])\n\nconst navigateToStep = (stepNumber: number) => {\n  formStore.setCurrentStep(stepNumber)\n  router.push(`/app/form/step-${stepNumber}`)\n}\n\nconst handleSaveDraft = () => {\n  draftStore.saveDraft()\n  // 显示保存成功提示\n  useToast().success('草稿已保存')\n}\n\nconst handleSync = async () => {\n  if (!syncStore.canSync) {\n    useToast().warning('同步次数已用完，请升级到付费版')\n    return\n  }\n\n  if (confirm('确定要同步到DS-160官网吗？这将消耗1次同步机会。')) {\n    await syncStore.syncToDS160()\n  }\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n### 22. components/app/StepItem.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <button\n    class=\"w-full flex items-center p-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200\"\n    :class=\"{\n      'bg-primary-50 border-2 border-primary-500': isCurrent,\n      'bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 hover:bg-primary-50/50': !isCurrent,\n      'opacity-60': !isCompleted && !isCurrent\n    }\"\n    @click=\"$emit('click')\"\n  >\n    <!-- 步骤图标/状态 -->\n    <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 mr-3\">\n      <div\n        class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\"\n        :class=\"{\n          'bg-green-500': isCompleted,\n          'bg-primary-600': isCurrent && !isCompleted,\n          'bg-gray-300': !isCurrent && !isCompleted\n        }\"\n      >\n        <Icon\n          v-if=\"isCompleted\"\n          name=\"mdi:check\"\n          class=\"w-5 h-5 text-white\"\n        />\n        <span v-else class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">\n          {{ step.number }}\n        </span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 步骤信息 -->\n    <div class=\"flex-1 text-left\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n        <h4\n          class=\"text-sm font-semibold\"\n          :class=\"{\n            'text-primary-900': isCurrent,\n            'text-gray-900': !isCurrent\n          }\"\n        >\n          {{ step.title }}\n        </h4>\n        <Icon\n          v-if=\"step.hasWarnings\"\n          name=\"mdi:alert-circle\"\n          class=\"w-4 h-4 text-warning-500 ml-2\"\n          title=\"包含高风险字段\"\n        />\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mt-0.5\">\n        {{ step.description }}\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 箭头 -->\n    <Icon\n      v-if=\"isCurrent\"\n      name=\"mdi:chevron-right\"\n      class=\"w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0\"\n    />\n  </button>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport type { StepInfo } from '~/types'\n\ndefineProps<{\n  step: StepInfo\n  isCurrent: boolean\n  isCompleted: boolean\n}>()\n\ndefineEmits<{\n  click: []\n}>()\n</script>\n```\n\n### 23. components/app/MobileStepNavigation.vue\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-white\">\n    <!-- 上一步 -->\n    <button\n      :disabled=\"currentStep === 1\"\n      class=\"flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors\"\n      :class=\"\n        currentStep === 1\n          ? 'text-gray-400 cursor-not-allowed'\n          : 'text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50'\n      \"\n      @click=\"goToPreviousStep\"\n    >\n      <Icon name=\"mdi:chevron-left\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-1\" />\n      上一步\n    </button>\n\n    <!-- 当前步骤指示 -->\n    <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n      <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900\">\n        {{ currentStep }}/12\n      </span>\n      <button\n        class=\"p-2 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg\"\n        @click=\"showStepSelector = true\"\n      >\n        <Icon name=\"mdi:menu\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-gray-600\" />\n      </button>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 下一步 -->\n    <button\n      :disabled=\"currentStep === 12\"\n      class=\"flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors\"\n      :class=\"\n        currentStep === 12\n          ? 'text-gray-400 cursor-not-allowed'\n          : 'text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50'\n      \"\n      @click=\"goToNextStep\"\n    >\n      下一步\n      <Icon name=\"mdi:chevron-right\" class=\"w-5 h-5 ml-1\" />\n    </button>\n\n    <!-- 步骤选择器Modal -->\n    <Modal v-model=\"showStepSelector\" title=\"选择步骤\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\">\n        <button\n          v-for=\"n in 12\"\n          :key=\"n\"\n          class=\"p-3 rounded-lg border-2 text-left transition-colors\"\n          :class=\"{\n            'border-primary-500 bg-primary-50': n === currentStep,\n            'border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300': n !== currentStep\n          }\"\n          @click=\"navigateToStep(n)\"\n        >\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">步骤 {{ n }}</span>\n            <Icon\n              v-if=\"formStore.isStepCompleted(n)\"\n              name=\"mdi:check-circle\"\n              class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-500\"\n            />\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">{{ getStepTitle(n) }}</span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </Modal>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nconst formStore = useFormStore()\nconst router = useRouter()\n\nconst currentStep = computed(() => formStore.currentStep)\nconst showStepSelector = ref(false)\n\nconst goToPreviousStep = () => {\n  if (currentStep.value > 1) {\n    navigateToStep(currentStep.value - 1)\n  }\n}\n\nconst goToNextStep = () => {\n  if (currentStep.value < 12) {\n    navigateToStep(currentStep.value + 1)\n  }\n}\n\nconst navigateToStep = (step: number) => {\n  formStore.setCurrentStep(step)\n  router.push(`/app/form/step-${step}`)\n  showStepSelector.value = false\n}\n\nconst getStepTitle = (step: number): string => {\n  const titles: Record<number, string> = {\n    1: '个人信息',\n    2: '护照信息',\n    3: '联系方式',\n    4: '旅行信息',\n    5: '旅行伙伴',\n    6: '美国联系人',\n    7: '家庭信息',\n    8: '工作/教育',\n    9: '安全问题(1)',\n    10: '安全问题(2)',\n    11: '以往旅行',\n    12: '照片与确认'\n  }\n  return titles[step] || ''\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n由于输出长度限制，我需要继续在下一个回复中完成剩余的组件和stores。\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: User\n\n\n================================================================================\n✅ 开发流程完成！\n================================================================================\n\n================================================================================\n📤 推送代码到GitHub...\n================================================================================\n$ git init\n$ git add .\n$ git commit -m \"Initial commit: DS-160 Helper MVP by AG2 Team\"\n⚠️  命令执行警告: \n$ git branch -M main\n$ git remote add origin https://ruoqianfengshao:***TOKEN***@github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git\n$ git push -u origin main --force\n⚠️  命令执行警告: error: src refspec main does not match any\nerror: failed to push some refs to 'https://github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git'\n\n\n✅ 代码已推送到GitHub!\n🔗 查看仓库: https://github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git\